lace%20of%20residence'%20on%20the%20nominating%20petition%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20five-page%20notice%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Constitution's%20provisions%20governing%20federal%20elections%20make%20no%20such%20demand%20for%20an%20address%2C%20the%20notice%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20provides%20what%20the%20qualifications%20of%20presidents%20are%2C%20and%20the%20states%20can't%20add%20to%20those%20qualifications%2C%26quot%3B%20Kennedy%20attorney%20Gary%20L.%20Donovan%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25042746-rfk-jr-albany-notice-of-appeal-20240814%2F%3Fembed%3D1%26responsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22RFK%20Jr.%20Albany%20Notice%20of%20Appeal%202024.08.14%20(Hosted%20by%20DocumentCloud)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22905%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy's%20notice%20of%20appeal%20was%20filed%20in%20response%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25042742-rfk-jr-albany-decision-20240812%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%2034-page%20decision%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20New%20York%20State%20Supreme%20Court%20Justice%20Christina%20Ryba%2C%20who%20found%20on%20Monday%20that%20the%20independent%20candidate%20lives%20in%20California%20but%20falsely%20claimed%20to%20live%20about%2040%20miles%20north%20of%20Manhattan%20in%20upstate%20Westchester%20County.%20The%20falsehood%20invalidated%20Kennedy's%20nominating%20petitions%2C%20the%20judge%20found.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spare%20bedroom%20Kennedy%20rented%2C%20without%20a%20lease%2C%20in%20a%20house%20owned%20by%20friends%20in%20Katonah%2C%20New%20York%2C%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bbonafide%20and%20legitimate%20residence%2C%20but%20merely%20a%20'sham'%20address%20that%20he%20assumed%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20maintaining%20his%20voter%20registration%26quot%3B%20and%20furthering%20his%20political%20aspirations%2C%20she%20wrote%20in%20her%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20actually%20lives%20in%20California%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20%26quot%3BCurb%20Your%20Enthusiasm%26quot%3B%20actor%20Cheryl%20Hines%2C%20the%20judge%20said%20she%20found%20after%20presiding%20over%20a%20four-day%20non-jury%20trial%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20testimony%20at%20the%20trial%2C%20Kennedy%20%26quot%3Bwas%20shown%20a%20photo%20of%20the%20spare%20bedroom%20he%20claimed%20to%20be%20renting%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote%20in%20her%20decision.%20%26quot%3BHe%20testified%20that%20none%20of%20the%20furniture%20or%20bedding%20was%20his.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20testified%2C%20too%2C%20that%20he%20plans%20to%20someday%20move%20into%20the%20spare%20bedroom%20with%20Hines%2C%20his%20extensive%20book%20collection%2C%20and%20his%20many%20exotic%20pets%20%E2%80%94%20including%20his%20pet%20raven%20%E2%80%94%20once%20Hines%20retires%20from%20acting%2C%20%26quot%3Bif%20that%20is%20convenient%20at%20the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20a%20transcript%20excerpt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20not%2C%20I'll%20find%20a%20house%20nearby%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%20from%20the%20witness%20stand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221f57ba2-1169-4ac4-90ee-98b957711796%5C%22%3EA%20'bizarre'%20appeal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20bizarre%2C%26quot%3B%20former%20Democratic%20NY%20state%20Sen.%20Martin%20Connor%2C%20who%20has%20practiced%20election%20law%20for%20fifty%20years%2C%20said%20when%20told%20of%20Kennedy's%20notice%20of%20appeal%20and%20its%20claim%20that%20the%20Constitution%20protects%20him%20from%20having%20to%20state%20an%20address.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidency%20under%20New%20York%20election%20law%20has%20gotten%20very%20loose%20over%20the%20years%2C%20Connor%20said.%20Still%2C%20candidates%20need%20to%20declare%20a%20specific%20address%20somewhere%20in%20the%20country%20%26quot%3Bthat's%20provably%20yours%20and%20more%20than%20just%20a%20mail%20drop%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EElection%20officials%20need%20to%20know%20where%20to%20contact%20a%20candidate%20if%20there%20are%20defects%20in%20their%20petition%2C%20and%20if%20someone%20wants%20to%20challenge%20the%20petition%20in%20court%20they%20need%20to%20know%20where%20to%20serve%20the%20papers%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20real%20question%20is%2C%20without%20an%20address%2C%20how%20do%20we%20know%20who%20the%20hell%20you%20are%3F%26quot%3B%20Connor%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20there%20are%20more%20than%20one%20John%20Smiths%20%E2%80%94%20or%20more%20than%20one%20Robert%20Kennedy%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20arguing%20that%20the%20Constitution%20does%20not%20require%20presidential%20candidates%20to%20state%20their%20addresses%20%E2%80%94%20and%20so%20neither%20should%20the%20states%20%E2%80%94%20Connor%20noted%20that%20the%20founding%20fathers%20left%20the%20specifics%20of%20how%20to%20run%20elections%20to%20the%20states.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Constitution%20doesn't%20mention%20how%20you%20get%20on%20the%20ballot%20in%20New%20York%20or%20in%20any%20state%2C%20either.%20Yet%20every%20state%20has%20rules%20for%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20had%20first%20claimed%20last%20month%20that%20New%20York's%20election%20law%20is%20unconstitutional%20insofar%20as%20it%20requires%20an%20address%20from%20candidates%20submitting%20nominating%20petitions%20for%20president%20and%20vice-president.%20The%20Constitution's%20provisions%20governing%20federal%20elections%20make%20no%20mention%20of%20%26quot%3Bplace%20of%20residence%26quot%3B%20requirement%2C%26quot%3B%20his%20lawyers%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20judge%20rejected%20the%20claim%20shortly%20before%20the%20trial%20started.%20Afterward%2C%20she%20did%20not%20mince%20words%20in%20declaring%20that%20Kennedy's%20purported%20address%20was%20a%20fiction.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20wrote%20in%20her%20decision%20that%20%26quot%3BKennedy's%20testimony%20that%20none%20of%20the%20furniture%2C%20bedding%2C%20and%20other%20decorative%20items%20in%20the%20spare%20bedroom%20belonged%20to%20him%2C%20as%20well%20as%20his%20testimony%20that%20his%20wife%20and%20family%2C%20his%20extensive%20book%20collection%2C%20and%20his%20wide%20assortment%20of%20domestic%20and%20exotic%20pets%20all%20remained%20in%20California%2C%20was%20further%20compelling%20evidence%20that%20Kennedy%20lacks%20the%20necessary%20physical%20presence%20and%20intent%20to%20remain%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25042742-rfk-jr-albany-decision-20240812%2F%3Fembed%3D1%26responsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22700%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22RFK%20Jr.%20Albany%20decision%202024.08.12%20(Hosted%20by%20DocumentCloud)%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22902%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20challenging%20the%2070-year-old%20candidate's%20nominating%20petition%20was%20filed%20late%20last%20month%20by%20a%20group%20of%20New%20York%20voters%20backed%20by%20Clear%20Choice%20Action%2C%20a%20Democrat-aligned%20super%20PAC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20group%20has%20identified%2018%20states%20where%20Kennedy's%20presence%20on%20the%20ballot%20could%20face%20similar%20challenges%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.motherjones.com%2Fpolitics%2F2024%2F08%2Frobert-f-kennedy-jr-new-york-residency-case-clear-choice-pac%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaccording%20to%20Mother%20Jones.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frfk-jr-claims-unconstitutional-to-make-him-say-where-lives-2024-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%