nt%20at%20first%2C%20but%20eventually%20got%20excited%20about%20a%20new%20adventure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20when%20the%20school%20year%20ended%20in%20May%2C%20we%20packed%20our%20bags%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-first-time-visitors-dubai-from-locals-live-there-2024%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20only%20been%20a%20few%20months%2C%20but%20I%20love%20it%20here.%20It's%20convenient%20to%20quickly%20get%20services%20like%20food%20delivery%2C%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20I've%20ever%20lived%20anywhere%20where%20I%20felt%20so%20safe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20not%20our%20first%20time%20relocating.%20In%202015%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20moved%20to%20London%20for%2015%20months%20for%20his%20work.%20While%20it%20was%20an%20amazing%20experience%2C%20our%20move%20to%20the%20UK%20was%20much%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdubai-what-to-know-before-visiting-first-time-from-america-2022-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eharder%20than%20it%20was%20in%20Dubai%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20found%20it%20difficult%20to%20find%20the%20things%20that%20I%20was%20used%20to%20in%20America%20when%20living%20in%20London.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22dac9686a-1933-4faf-9b07-1e0ac83dc2ff%5C%22%3EWe%20were%20surprised%20to%20see%20so%20many%20American%20fast-food%20chains%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224545%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Three%20kids%20sipping%20on%20chocolate%20milk%20in%20a%20restaurant%20in%20Dubai.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bc564eb4912df3ae1b773e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223409%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMiller%20was%20pleased%20to%20find%20a%20variety%20of%20food%20options%20in%20Dubai.%3Cp%3EKatie%20Miller%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cheesecake%20Factory%20is%20my%20favorite%20because%2C%20being%20a%20true%20Texas%20girl%2C%20I%20can%20get%2