%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epetition%3C%2Fa%3E%20alleges%20that%20Gunn%20established%20the%20governing%20body%20that%20managed%20the%20qualifier%20and%20that%20Gunn's%20husband%20Samuel%20Free%20may%20have%20been%20part%20of%20the%20%26quot%3Bselection%20panel%26quot%3B%20for%20Australia's%20representatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Gunn's%20qualifying%20process%20is%20relatively%20simple%20to%20trace%20%E2%80%94%20here's%20a%20breakdown%20of%20how%20she%20qualified%20for%20the%20Paris%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da0f32de-1dde-4344-8361-6bdf882d650d%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20World%20DanceSport%20Federation%20announced%20the%20breaking%20qualifying%20process%20in%202022%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparis-2024-olympics-closing-ceremony-important-moments-explained-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParis%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%20presented%20breaking%20in%20partnership%20with%20the%20World%20DanceSport%20Federation%20(WDSF)%2C%20adding%20it%20to%20the%20games%20after%20its%20debut%20at%20the%20Summer%20Youth%20Olympic%20Games%20in%202018%2C%20according%20to%20the%20official%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fen%2Fparis-2024%2Fsports%2Fbreaking%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOlympics%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20WDSF%20announced%20the%20qualifying%20system%20in%20April%202022.%20There%20were%2032%20spots%20%E2%80%94%2016%20B-Girls%20and%2016%20B-Boys%20%E2%80%94%20available%20in%20the%20games%2C%20and%20three%20different%20ways%20to%20qualify.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Col%3E%3Cli%3EBreakers%20could%20qualify%20at%20the%20WDSF%20World%20Championships%20held%20in%20Belgium%20in%20September%202023.%20There%20were%20two%20spots%20available%20%E2%80%94%20one%20man%20and%20one%20woman.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBreakers%20could%20also%20qualify%20through%20a%20continental%20qualifying%20event%2C%20each%20of%20which%20had%20two%20spots%20available%20for%20a%20man%20and%20a%20woman.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20remaining%2020%20spots%20were%20up%20for%20grabs%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Folympics.com%2Fen%2Folympic-qualifier-series%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOlympic%20qualifier%20series%3C%2Fa%3E%20events%20in%20Shanghai%20and%20Budapest%20in%20May%20and%20June%202024.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Fol%3E%3Cp%3EAustralia's%20regional%20qualifying%20event%20was%20the%202023%20WDSF%20Breaking%20Oceania%20Championship%2C%20which%20was%20held%20in%20Sydney%20in%20October%202023.%20The%20regional%20organization%20Ausbreaking%20organized%20the%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223101%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rachael%20gun%2C%20raygun%2C%20competing%20at%20the%20wdsf%20oceana%20breaking%20championships.%20she's%20wearing%20baggy%20jeans%2C%20sneakers%2C%20and%20a%20red%20windbreaker%2C%20leaning%20on%20her%20head%20and%20hands%20with%20one%20lg%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20another%20up%20in%20the%20air%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bcf8df955b01c3294eb1a0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222326%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachael%20Gun%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BRaygun%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20competing%20at%20the%202023%20WDSF%20Oceania%20Breaking%20Championships.%3Cp%3EMark%20Kolbe%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.smh.com.au%2Fculture%2Fcelebrity%2Fthe-inside-story-of-how-raygun-broke-into-the-olympics-20240812-p5k1mg.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESydney%20Morning%20Herald%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20current%20Ausbreaking%20president%20Lowe%20Napalan%20%E2%80%94%20himself%20a%20breaker%20%E2%80%94%20established%20the%20organization%20in%202019.%20Breaking%20was%20confirmed%20as%20a%202024%20Olympic%20sport%20in%20December%202020%2C%20and%20the%20organization%20(then%20called%20the%20Australian%20Breaking%20Association)%20began%20to%20take%20registrations%20for%20breakers%20interested%20in%20competing%20at%20the%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAusbreaking%20has%20maintained%20a%20national%20ranking%20system%20dating%20back%20to%202020.%20Gunn%20ranked%20first%20in%20the%20inaugural%202020%20ranking%2C%20then%20again%20in%202021.%20She%20placed%20second%20in%20both%202022%20and%202023%2C%20according%20to%20publicly%20available%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcircle-terrier-kpr6.squarespace.com%2Frankings%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erecords%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAusbreaking%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCxnGQytoTmW%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20September%202023%20Instagram%20post%20that%20registration%20was%20open%20for%20the%20Oceania%20championship.%20The%20organization%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCyh-pfSpk6u%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20judging%20panel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worlddancesport.org%2FCompetitions%2FOfficials%2FOceania-Championship-Sydney-Adult-Breaking-1vs1-B-Girls-60318%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecomposed%20of%20international%20breakers%3C%2Fa%3E%20(none%20from%20Australia)%20and%20headed%20up%20by%20Katsu%20One%20of%20Japan%2C%20on%20October%2018%2C%202023%20%E2%80%94%20meaning%20Free%20%3Cem%3Ewasn't%3C%2Fem%3E%20one%20of%20the%20judges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227e2c6c04-9a25-4f4b-ad96-0b500cc47d39%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EGunn%20qualified%20at%20the%20Oceania%20Championship%20in%20October%202023%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGunn%20competed%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worlddancesport.org%2FCompetitions%2FRanking%2FWorld-Championship-Leuven-Adult-Breaking-1vs1-b-girls-58289%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWDSF%20World%20Championship%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20September%202023%20%E2%80%94%20the%20first%20opportunity%20to%20earn%20a%20s