%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FCzQZdxSBdnW%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20post%20shared%20by%20AUSBreaking%20(%40ausbreaking)%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAustralia%20had%20the%20potential%20to%20send%20one%20more%20woman%20to%20the%20Olympics%20via%20the%20qualifier%20series%20events%20held%20in%20Shanghai%20and%20Budapest%20in%202024.%20The%20second%2C%20third%2C%20and%20fourth%20place%20B-Girls%20from%20the%20Oceania%20qualifier%20%E2%80%94%20Holy%20Molly%2C%20Hannah%2C%20and%20G-Clef%20%E2%80%94%20competed%2C%20but%20did%20not%20earn%20a%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220405980c-9889-412c-b5ea-50a84dcae280%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAusbreaking%20has%20released%20multiple%20statements%20refuting%20claims%20about%20Raygun's%20qualification%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Ausbreaking%20released%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-kUHK2zEu_%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estatement%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20the%20qualifying%20process%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20Oceania%20championships%20were%20judged%20using%20the%20same%20system%20as%20the%202024%20Olympics.%20The%20organization%20also%20condemned%20harassment%20against%20Gunn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20Rachael%20Gunn%20and%20Jeff%20Dunne%20emerged%20as%20the%20top%20performers%20in%20exactly%20the%20same%20process%2C%20securing%20their%20spots%20to%20represent%20Australia%20in%20Paris%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20reads.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20selection%20was%20based%20solely%20on%20their%20performance%20in%20their%20battles%20on%20that%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20organization%20released%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FC-puiJezEHe%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_web_copy_link%26igsh%3DMzRlODBiNWFlZA%3D%3D%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%