%2Fmumbai%2F2-cross-voting-congress-mlas-meet-shinde-trigger-buzz%2Farticleshow%2F112533928.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Apple%20is%20making%20enemies%20among%20creators%20by%20hitting%20Patreon%20with%20a%2030%25%20tax%20%E2%80%94%20but%20there's%20a%20loophole%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221440%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Apple's%20Tim%20Cook%20and%20Patreon's%20Jack%20Conte%20collaged%20side%20by%20side%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bd16c4b4912df3ae1bd219%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApple%20will%20take%2030%25%20of%20transactions%20made%20within%20Patreon's%20iOS%20app%20starting%20in%20November.%3Cp%3EJerod%20Harris%2FGetty%20Images%3B%20Justin%20Sullivan%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EPatreon%20must%20accept%20Apple's%2030%25%20fee%20on%20all%20in-app%20purchases%20starting%20in%20November%20or%20face%20removal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECreator-economy%20startups%20have%20been%20facing%20Apple's%20fees%20for%20years.%20Patreon%20just%20happened%20to%20be%20lucky.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECreators%20could%20potentially%20bypass%20the%20fee%20by%20directing%20transactions%20to%20Patreon's%20website.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20creator%20economy%20has%20a%20not-so-new%20bad%20guy%20in%20town%3A%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fredefining-creator-fan-relationship-patreon-launches-community-features-group-chat-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatreon%3C%2Fa%3E%20informed%20creators%20that%20starting%20in%20November%2C%20all%20in-app%20purchases%20made%20on%20the%20Patreon%20app%20would%20be%20subject%20to%20Apple's%2030%25%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatreon%20has%20since%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.patreon.com%2Farticles%2Funderstanding-apple-requirements-for-patreon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epresented%3C%2Fa%3E%20two%20options%20to%20creators%20%E2%80%94%20either%20automatically%20raise%20in-app%20prices%20to%20cover%20the%20fee%20or%20creators%20will%20have%20to%20eat%20the%20fee%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20there%20is%20a%20third%20option%20that%20Patreon%20isn't%20promoting.%20Creators%20could%20(and%20likely%20will)%20recommend%20that%20their%20fans%20make%20any%20transactions%20on%20Patreon's%20website%2C%20rather%20than%20the%20iPhone%20app.%20That%20means%20creators%20%E2%80%94%20and%20Patreon%20%E2%80%94%20both%20wouldn't%20lose%20money%20to%20Apple.%20Apps%20like%20Substack%20and%20Netflix%20already%20operate%20in%20this%20way%2C%20where%20subscriptions%20are%20handled%20off-app%20and%20once%20a%20user%20logs%20in%2C%20they%20can%20access%20their%20subscriptions%20within%20the%20iOS%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20years%2C%20Patreon%20had%20been%20able%20to%20skirt%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20fees.%20In%202021%2C%20Patreon%20CEO%20Jack%20Conte%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F22543655%2Fpatreon-ceo-decoder-interview-jack-conte%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20The%20Verge%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Apple%20had%20not%20told%20the%20startup%20explicitly%20that%20it%20needed%20to%20pay%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20changed%20at%20the%20end%20of%202023%20when%20Apple%20first%20came%20down%20on%20Patreon%20by%20enforcing%20its%2030%25%20fee%20on%20any%20commerce%20purchases%20made%20in%20the%20Patreon%20app.%20And%20now%2C%20Apple%20is%20expanding%20that%20to%20all%20transactions%20made%20within%20the%20Patreon%20app%2C%20including%20subscriptions.%20If%20Patreon%20doesn't%20oblige%2C%20Apple%20is%20threatening%20to%20remove%20the%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d640a41d-b9a0-42bb-b7a3-6a82a9d5b6ee%5C%22%3ECreators%20are%20frustrated%20and%20confused%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCreators%20are%20freaking%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20former%20Patreon%20exec%20Avi%20Gandhi.%20%26quot%3BWe%20live%20in%20the%20age%20of%20digital%20gods%2C%20and%20Apple's%20App%20Store%20is%20certainly%20one%20of%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAcross%20Reddit%20and%20Discord%2C%20Patreon%20users%20are%20vocalizing%20their%20frustrations%20with%20Apple%20and%20Patreon%20alike.%20Some%20want%20Patreon%20to%20scrap%20its%20iOS%20app%20entirely%2C%20others%20want%20Patreon%20to%20eat%20the%20fee%20(which%20wouldn't%20be%20financially%20possible)%2C%20and%20then%20there%20are%20those%20who%20are%20just%20angry%20with%20Apple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BApple%20has%20gone%20from%20'Think%20Different'%20to%20'Think%20Extortionate%2C'%26quot%3B%20Laurel%20Kilgour%2C%20a%20research%20manager%20for%20the%20American%20Economic%20Liberties%20Project%2C%20wrote%20in%20a%20press%20release%20shared%20on%20Wednesday.%20%26quot%3BThis%20outrageous%2030%25%20revenue%20cut%20%E2%80%94%20nearly%202.5%20times%20more%20than%20Patreon's%20most%20premium%20membership%20tier%20%E2%80%94%20is%20especially%20egregious%20given%20Apple's%20ongoing%2C%20worldwide%20legal%20battles%20over%20its%20monopolistic%20practices.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20rest%20assured%2C%20creators%20will%20find%20ways%20around%20Apple's%20fee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlready%2C%20creators%20are%20discussing%20ways%20that%20they%20can%20circumvent%20Apple's%20fee%20by%20having%20their%20fans%20make%20transactions%20outside%20of%20the%20Patreon%20iOS%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPatreon%20is%20not%20explicitly%20promoting%20that%20solution%20for%20creators%2C%20likely%20to%20try%20to%20not%20ruffle%20the%20feathers%20of%20Apple%20any%20further.%20And%20it%20needs%20its%20iOS%20app%20because%20that%20is%20where%20users%20are.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20do%20this%2C%20Apple%20might%20kick%20us%20out%20of%20the%20App%20Store%2C%20which%20would%20be%20terrible%20for%20creators%20and%20terrible%20for%20Patreon%20because%20iOS%20is%20actually%20now%20the%20most%20used%20platform%20for%20communities%20on%20Patreon%2C%26quot%3B%20Conte%20said%20in%20a%20YouTube%20video%20posted%20on%20August%2012.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EApple%20and%20Patreon%20did%20not%20provide%20comment%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220c49957c-a6d0-4d9c-9389-f6d3cb78275a%5C%22%3EApple%20isn't%20seen%20as%20a%20friend%20in%20the%20creator%20economy%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EPatreon%20isn't%20the%20only%20startup%20creators%20are%20using%20to%20build%20businesses%20around%20their%20communities%20and%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20platforms%2C%20like%20Kajabi%2C%20Mighty%20Networks%2C%20Passes%2C%20and%20Substack%20are%20either%20already%20being%20taxed%20by%20Apple%20or%20navigating%20these%20issues%20in%20real%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20what%20happens%20when%20you%20build%20on%20rented%20space%20versus%20owned%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20Kajabi%20CEO%20Ahad%20Khan%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20building%20your%20business%20on%20a%20platform%20that%20can%20change%20revenue%20share%20policies%20kind%20of%20whenever%20they%20feel%20like%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20instance%2C%20Kajabi%20helps%20creators%20make%20branded%20mobile%20apps%2C%20but%20creators%20understand%20that%20if%20they%20put%20that%20app%20on%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%20and%20there%20are%20in-app%20transactions%2C%20they%20will%20be%20taxed%20by%20Apple.%20Each%20creator%20has%20to%20decide%20what%20makes%20sense%20for%20their%20business%2C%20in%20the%20end%2C%20Khan%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-creators-turn-audiences-into-community-startups-patreon-discord-kajabi-2023-11%23mighty-networks-offers-an-ai-assistant-tool-to-help-creators-manage-their-communities-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMighty%20Networks%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20helps%20creators%20make%20apps%20listed%20on%20the%20Apple%20App%20Store%20and%20has%20had%20to%20deal%20with%20Apple's%20fees%20for%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20in-app%20purchases%20are%20triggered%20on%20any%20Mighty%20network%2C%20we%20don't%20take%20a%20cut%20at%20all%2C%26quot%3B%20CEO%20Gina%20Bianchini%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BSo%20we%20essentially%20give%20back%20anything%20that%20we%20would%20be%20taking%20to%20the%20creator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20other%20platforms%2C%20like%20Substack%20and%20Passes%2C%20are%20navigating%20these%20questions%20as%20they%20build%20out%20their%20mobile%20app%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESubstack's%20cofounder%20Hamish%20McKenzie%20wrote%20that%20the%20startup%20doesn't%20%26quot%3Bthink%20that%20Apple%20should%20be%20wholly%20blamed%26quot%3B%20and%20is%20working%20with%20Apple%20to%20bring%20in-app%20purchases%20to%20the%20Substack%20app.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20doing%20everything%20in%20our%20power%20to%20make%20the%20implementation%20of%20in-app%20purchases%20as%20creator-friendly%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20McKenzie%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPasses%20CEO%20Lucy%20Guo%20told%20BI%20that%20its%20iOS%20app%20would%20have%20higher%20prices%20than%20on%20its%20website%20to%20offset%20the%20impact%20on%20creators'%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20that%20Apple%20should%20make%20exceptions%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20creators%2C%26quot%3B%20Guo%20said%20in%20an%20email.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Apple%20tax%20hurts%20individual%20creators%20who%20rely%20on%20Passes%20as%20their%20main%20source%20of%20income.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuffice%20to%20say%2C%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20the%20creator%20economy%20and%20Apple%2C%20things%20are%20%3Cem%3Ecomplicated.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20actually%20fault%20Apple%2C%26quot%3B%20Bianchini%20said.%20%26quot%3BApple's%20not%20the%20most%20evil%20thing%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20not%20everybody's%20friend%20either.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fapple-makes-creator-enemies-with-patreon-fees-but