%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20man%20filed%20a%20wrongful-death%20lawsuit%20against%20Disney%20in%20February.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20lawsuit%20says%20the%20man's%20wife%20died%20of%20a%20severe%20allergic%20reaction%20after%20eating%20at%20Disney%20Springs.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDisney%20wants%20the%20lawsuit%20dismissed%20because%20the%20husband%20signed%20up%20for%20Disney%2B%20in%202019.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20asked%20a%20court%20to%20dismiss%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoctor-dies-allergic-reaction-disney-world-restaurant-orlando-meal-lawsuit-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrongful-death%20lawsuit%20filed%20by%20a%20widowed%20husband%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20he%20signed%20up%20for%20a%20free%20trial%20of%20Disney%2B%20and%20purchased%20tickets%20to%20its%20theme%20park%2C%20according%20to%20court%20documents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJeffrey%20J.%20Piccolo%20first%20filed%20the%20lawsuit%20on%20behalf%20of%20his%20deceased%20wife%2C%20Kanokporn%20Tangsuan%2C%20in%20Central%20Florida%20in%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECourt%20documents%20said%20Tangsuan%20died%20on%20October%205%2C%202023%2C%20from%20a%20'%26quot%3Bsevere%20acute%20allergic%20reaction%26quot%3B%20after%20dining%20at%20Raglan%20Road%20Irish%20Pub%20and%20Restaurant%20at%20Disney%20Springs%2C%20which%20is%20an%20outdoor%20shopping%20and%20entertainment%20complex%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Splitsville%20Luxury%20Lanes%20in%20Disney%20Springs.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6660c68cd0b8e1c832cc4be5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222533%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20photo%20showing%20restaurants%20and%20shops%20in%20Disney%20Springs%20at%20Walt%20Disney%20World.%20%3Cp%3EJeff%20Greenberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETangsuan%20had%20severe%20dairy%20and%20nut%20alle