e%2C%20regulation%2C%20or%20other%20legal%20or%20equitable%20basis%2C'%26quot%3B%20Disney%20said%20in%20court%20documents.%20%26quot%3BThis%20broad%20language%20covers%20Piccolo's%20claims%20against%20WDPR.%20Because%20the%20parties%20agreed%20to%20arbitrate%20these%20claims%2C%20the%20court%20should%20compel%20arbitration%20and%20stay%20the%20proceedings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Disney%2B%20login%20page%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bcf53e955b01c3294eaeb1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Terms%20of%20Use%20on%20Disney%2B%20include%20a%20Subscriber%20Agreement%20with%20a%26quot%3Bbinding%20arbitration%20clause.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3ESOPA%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e5638dc7-02a1-4f95-9191-3f3b0b5b9d95%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPiccolo's%20attorneys%20have%20called%20Disney's%20argument%20'fatally%20flawed'%20and%20bordering%20on%20'surreal'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20court%20document%20filed%20this%20month%2C%20Piccolo's%20legal%20representatives%20criticized%20Disney's%20argument%20as%20%26quot%3Bfatally%20flawed%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpreposterous.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPiccolo's%20lawyers%20say%20Disney's%20argument%20is%20%26quot%3Bbased%20on%20the%20incredible%20argument%20that%20any%20person%20who%20signs%20up%20for%20a%20Disney%2B%20account%2C%20even%20free%20trials%20that%20are%20not%20extended%20beyond%20the%20trial%20period%2C%20will%20have%20forever%20waived%20the%20right%20to%20a%20jury%20trial%20enjoyed%20by%20them%20and%20any%20future%20Estate%20to%20which%20they%20are%20associated...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20argument%20that%20its%20Terms%20of%20Use%20extend%20to%20personal%20injury%20and%20wrongful%20death%20claims%20%26quot%3Bno%20matter%20how%20far%20removed%26quot%3B%20from%20Disney%2B%20%26quot%3Bborders%20on%20th