20run%20and%20walked%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20different%20Hoka%20models%2C%20and%20the%20Cliftons%20hit%20the%20best%20balance%20of%20comfort%2C%20support%2C%20and%20breathability%20while%20also%20incorporating%20all%20of%20the%20brand's%20signature%20features%2C%20making%20them%20the%20best%20shoe%20for%20most%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Cliftons%20are%20known%20for%20being%20well-balanced%20between%20being%20cushioned%20yet%20responsive%3B%20they%20provide%20soft%20support%20for%20achy%20joints%20but%20you%20don't%20get%20bogged%20down%20in%20the%20plushness.%20While%20past%20models%20have%20been%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bclunky%2C%26quot%3B%20Hoka%20has%20answered%20this%20call%20by%20giving%20the%209s%20a%20newer%20CMEVA%20foam%20that%20is%20more%20lightweight%20but%20also%203mm%20thicker%2C%20so%20it'll%20give%20even%20softer%20of%20a%20cradle%20without%20feeling%20heavy%20underfoot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20shoes%20are%20also%20designed%20with%20Hoka's%20trademark%20early%20stage%20meta-rocker%20design%20to%20help%20your%20foot%20naturally%20roll%20through%20easier%2C%20which%20makes%20them%20a%20great%20running%20shoe%20for%20beginners.%20And%20they%20come%20in%20fun%20(and%20plentiful)%20colorways%20so%20anyone%20can%20find%20a%20style%20that%20matches%20their%20vibe.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Clifton's%20hit%20the%20sweet%20spot%20for%20most%20people%2C%20if%20you%20want%20a%20higher-cushion%20Hoka%2C%20I'd%20recommend%20the%20Bondi%20(below)%20and%20if%20you%20overpronate%2C%20opt%20for%20the%20Gaviota%20(below).%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20cushioning%3A%20Hoka%20Bondi%208%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20cushioned%20Hoka%20sneakers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bcfeefb4912df3ae1bc484%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAlong%20with%20the%20Cliftons%2C%20the%20Bondi%20line%20is%20one%20of%20Hoka's%20best%20sellers.%20I've%20run%20in%20both%20(in%20current%20models%20and%20past)%2C%20and%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20ways%2C%20the%20Bondi%20and%20Clifton%20are%20very%20similar%20shoes.%20Both%20have%20Hoka's%20signature%20early-stage%20meta-rocker%20and%20EVA%20midsole%20foam.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20Bondi%20are%20markedly%20more%20cushioned%20than%20the%20Cliftons.%20That%20means%20when%20you%20run%20in%20the%20Bondi%2C%20your%20footfall%20will%20feel%20softer%20and%20more%20forgiving.%20This%20is%20great%20for%20people%20who%20otherwise%20experience%20knee%20pain%2C%20shin%20splints%2C%20or%20any%20running%20injuries%20that%20result%20from%20impact%20and%20shock.%20This%20is%20also%20great%20for%20people%20who%20stand%20all%20day%2C%20like%20nurses%20and%20store%20clerks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20like%20a%20snappy%2C%20responsive%20shoe%20that%20lets%20you%20push%20off%20the%20ground%20fast%2C%20you'll%20probably%20be%20happier%20with%20the%20Cliftons%20(or%20one%20of%20Hoka's%20speed%20models%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-72163-20%26h%3Dac724d2bb3c6b646b613bfdffa212ebeb99ba845ab3f9205fdccf25fda878436%26postID%3D66a27796c79d31931d85ff02%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-hokas%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hoka.com%252Fen%252Fus%252Fwomens-everyday-running-shoes%252Fmach-x%252F1141451.html%253Fdwvar_1141451_color%253DCRSCL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMach%20X%3C%2Fa%3E).%20That%20said%2C%20Hoka%20has%20done%20a%20lot%20to%20deliver%20the%20extra%20cushioning%20without%20the%20downsides%3A%20They've%20shaved%20weight%20to%20keep%20the%20Bondi%20weighing%20just%208.9%20ounces%20and%20included%20a%20rear%20crash%20pad%20that%20helps%20heel%20strikers%20transition%20to%20the%20forefoot%20quickly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20have%20an%20engineered%20mesh%20upper%20which%20is%20highly%20breathable%3B%20a%20plush%2C%20foam%20heel%20collar%3B%20and%20a.%20Despite%20being%20super%20cushy%2C%20Hoka's%20done%20a%20great%20job%20shaving%20weight%20off%20and%20the%20Bondi%20only%20log%20in%20at%208.9%20ounces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20love%20that%20the%20Bondi%208%20also%20comes%20in%20a%20whopping%2020%20colors%2C%20the%20majority%20of%20which%20are%20downright%20fun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20stability%3A%20Hoka%20Gaviota%205%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20neon%20yellow%20walking%20shoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669ebd1e0790490181858b0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%C2%A0If%20you%20want%20the%20max%20cushion%20the%20Bondi%20provides%20but%20need%20a%20stability%20shoe%2C%20I%20love%20running%20and%20walking%20in%20the%20Gaviota.%20Stability%20shoes%20are%20helpful%20if%20your%20foot%20rolls%20inward%20as%20it%20strikes%20and%20pushes%20off%20the%20ground%20%E2%80%94%20known%20as%20overpronation.%20They're%20crafted%20with%20more%20support%20under%20the%20arch%20of%20the%20feet%20to%20keep%20your%20foot%20flat%20as%20it%20rolls%20through%2C%20which%20in%20turn%20can%20help%20you%20avoid%20pain%20and%20collapsed%20arches%20in%20the%20long%20run.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaviota%205%20is%20equipped%20with%20a%20stabilizing%20H-Frame%2C%20Hoka's%20specialized%20technology%20that%20helps%20level%20out%20your%20foot%20while%20keeping%20the%20shoe%20lightweight.%20You%20can't%20feel%20the%20frame%20when%20you%20run%2C%20but%20it's%20enough%20to%20make%20running%20more%20comfortable%20for%20overpronators.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20the%20Gaviota%20is%20designed%20with%20a%20soft%2C%20EVA%20foam%20to%20give%20a%20plush%20and%20forgiving%20ride%20underfoot%20akin%20to%20the%20Bondi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20running%20and%20walking%20in%20the%20Gaviota%20for%20three%20months%2C%20I%20can%20attest%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-walking-shoes-for-women%5C%22%3Ecomfortable%20walking%20shoes%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20downright%20comfy%20with%20features%20like%20an%20ultra-plush%20collar%2C%20a%20highly%20breathable%20mesh%20upper%2C%20and%20a%20wider%20overall%20design.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20Hoka's%20other%20main%20stability%20model%2C%20the%20Ahari%2C%20which%20I've%20also%20tested%2C%20the%20Gaviota%20are%20more%20cushy%20underfoot%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20Bondi%2C%20while%20the%20Ahari%20have%20a%20cushioning%20level%20similar%20to%20the%20Cliftons.%20But%20the%20main%20difference%2C%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20is%20the%20Gaviota%20has%20an%20overall%20wider%2C%20more%20forgiving%20fit.%20That's%20in%20part%20because%20the%20Gaviota%20is%20designed%20with%20a%20wider%20midfoot%20and%20toe%20box%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20thanks%20to%20the%20creel%20jacquard%20upper%2C%20which%20is%20unconstrained%20and%20allows%20your%20foot%20to%20spread%20out%20more%20naturally.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20have%20a%20wider-than-average%20foot%20like%20I%20do%2C%20you'll%20love%20the%20fit%20(although%20note%20the%20Gaviota%20also%20comes%20in%20a%20true%20%26quot%3Bwide%26quot%3B%20option).%20And%20if%20you%20stand%20or%20walk%20a%20lot%20during%20the%20day%2C%20you'll%20also%20like%20this%20flexible%2C%20breathable%20fit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Hoka%20trail%20running%20shoes%3A%20Speedgoat%206%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20up%20close%20view%20on%20sneaker%20tread%20and%20the%20author%20wearing%20trail%20running%20sneakers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bd00f0955b01c3294eb6a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Hoka%20Speedgoats%20are%20unparalleled%20for%20trail%20running%20thanks%20to%20their%20cushioned%20midsole%20and%20mountain%20goat-like%20traction.%20I%20ran%20in%20(and%20loved)%20the%20Speedgoat%205s%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20but%20Hoka%20just%20released%20an%20upgraded%20model%2C%20the%20Speedgoat%206%2C%20and%20the%20changes%20have%20made%20the%20shoe%20an%20even%20better%20trail%20runner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Speedgoat%206%20uses%20an%20ultralight%20and%20more-responsive%20CMEVA%20midsole%20foam%20to%20create%20a%20super%20light%20shoe%20(8.2%20ounces)%20that%20lets%20you%20move%20fast%20through%20the%20mountains.%20This%20foam%20provides%20a%20balanced%20cushioning%2C%20which%2C%20in%20my%20experience%2C%20gives%20you%20enough%20squish%20and%20comfort%20for%20achy%20joints%20to%20feel%20supportive%20while%20maintaining%20and%20responsive%20push-off%20for%20fast%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Speedgoat%206%20has%20retained%20the%20aggressive%20traction%20this%20shoe%20is%20beloved%20for%2C%20with%20a%20refined%20Vibram%20Megagrip%20outsole%20and%20beefy%20lugs%20for%20technical%20terrain.%20It%20has%20a%20new%20lightweight%2C%20woven%20upper%20that%20is%20super%20breathable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20time%20I%20wore%20these%20trail%20runners%20out%2C%20I%20did%20struggle%20with%20the%20fit%20across%20the%20midfoot%20and%20toe%20box%20because%20of%20the%20seam%20taping%20around%20the%20lace%20area%20(which%20is%20ideal%20for%20durability%20of%20the%20shoe)%3B%20however%2C%20after%20the%20first%20three%20miles%2C%20the%20shoe%20started%20to%20loosen%20up%20and%20I%20had%20no%20issues%20with%20fit%20after.%20Another%20small%20but%20mighty%20upgrade%2C%20in%20my%20experience%3A%20The%20Speedgoat%205%20always%20gave%20me%20blisters%20on%20the%20heel%20on%20runs%20over%20five%20miles%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20broken%20in%20they%20were%3B%20luckily%2C%20this%20hasn't%20been%20an%20issue%20with%20the%20Speedgoat%206.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20downside%20is%20that%20the%20pattern%20and%20colors%20of%20the%20Speedgoat%206%2C%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20isn't%20that%20attractive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20Hoka%20hiking%20boots%3A%20Anacapa%20Mid%20GTX%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20close%20up%20view%20on%20the%20tread%20of%20a%20hiking%20boot%20and%20the%20author%20wearing%20Hoka%20hiking%20boots.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bd02bab4912df3ae1bc5da%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20like%20a%20cushy%2C%20supportive%20footbed%20on%20long%20hikes%2C%20you'll%20love%20Hoka's%20Anacapa%202%20Mid%20GTX.%20I%20wore%20the%20first%20iteration%20of%20these%20hiking%20boots%20straight%20out%20of%20the%20box%20onto%20a%205-mile%20hike%20in%20Colorado%20and%20they%20were%20incredibly%20comfortable%2C%20giving%20me%20no%20blisters%20or%20hot%20spots.%20Moreover%2C%20while%20my%20feet%20often%20start%20to%20ache%20when%20hiking%20in%20stiffer%20boots%2C%20in%20the%20Anacapas%2C%20my%20feet%20felt%20comforted%20throughout%20the%20hike.%20They%20aren't%20going%20to%20be%20as%20plush%20as%2C%20say%2C%20the%20Bondis%2C%20but%20they%20offer%20a%20slight%20amount%20of%20squish%20not%20often%20seen%20in%20hiking%20boots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Anacapa%202s%20are%20a%20mostly%20leather%20upper%2C%20weatherized%20with%20Gore-Tex%2C%20which%20is%20great%20for%20durability%20and%20waterproofing%20but%20the%20payoff%20is%20they%20retain%20some%20heat.%20That%20said%2C%20Hoka%20has%20incorporated%20mesh%20in%20the%20upper%20where%20possible%20for%20better%20breathability.%20The%20ankle%20and%20heel%20areas%20are%20cushioned%2C%20which%20is%20nice%20on%20your%20skin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20hiking%20boots%2C%20the%20Anacapas%20are%20pretty%20lightweight%20at%2014.7%20ounces.%20The%20lightweight%20EVA%20midsole%20trims%20weight%20while%20also%20providing%20a%20well-cushioned%20(but%20not%20muddy)%20ride.%20These%20hiking%20boots%20have%20a%20Vibram%20Megagrip%20outsole%20with%20deep%20lugs%20to%20dig%20into%20all%20kinds%20of%20trail%20and%20terrain.%20In%20my%20experience%2C%20these%20boots%20feel%20super%20secure%20on%20squirrelly%20terrain%20and%20I%20never%20feel%20like%20I'm%20going%20to%20slip%20out.%20Plus%2C%20they%20look%20cool.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20personally%20love%20a%20mid%20cut%20for%20ankle%20support%20on%20long%20hikes%2C%20but%20the%20Anacapa%202s%20do%20come%20in%20a%20low%20cut%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Gore-Tex%20free%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20waterproof%3A%20Hoka%20Transport%20GTX%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20in%20beige%20waterproof%20walking%20shoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6669ef20764df161125927f3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20waterproof%20sneakers%20are%20my%20choice%20for%20a%20lightweight%20alternative%20to%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-analytics-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2260%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Fbest-rain-boots-women%5C%22%3Erain%20boots%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20wore%20these%20on%20multiple%20walks%20and%20hikes%20and%20found%20them%20to%20be%20very%20comfortable.%20The%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-am-tid%3D%5C%22amcid-3lJ6MJV2ONY33mpA7bms%5C%22%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hoka.com%2Fen%2Fus%2Fwomens-lifestyle%2Ftransport-gtx%2F1133958.html%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%20sponsored%20noindex%5C%22%20data-am-orig-url%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dcf8d04eae2068db53b72b41f9775393addbbd4b26937bbcd427777af9caeaa1d%26amp%3Bu%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.