gle%20lace%20tucks%20away%20so%20the%20tail%20isn't%20flopping%20anywhere.%20I%20also%20love%20that%20the%20shoes%20come%20with%20traditional%20laces%20you%20can%20restring%20if%20desired%2C%20as%20I%20know%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20don't%20like%20the%20quick-toggle%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENote%20that%20these%20shoes%20have%20neutral%20stability%2C%20so%20they%20may%20not%20be%20supportive%20enough%20for%20people%20with%20high%20arches.%20And%20if%20you%20like%20a%20plush%20walking%20shoe%2C%20these%20might%20be%20too%20stiff%20for%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EBest%20slide%3A%20Hoka%20Ora%203%20Recovery%20Slide%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20wearing%20blue%20Hoka%20slides.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66bd0380b4912df3ae1bc622%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ERachael%20Schultz%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20suffering%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fbest-shoes-for-plantar-fasciitis%5C%22%3Eplantar%20fasciitis%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20need%20to%20ensure%20your%20feet%20never%20hit%20the%20ground%20without%20support%2C%20so%20slippers%20or%20house%20shoes%20are%20one%20of%20the%20top%20necessities.%20Hoka's%20Recovery%20Slides%20are%20my%20go-to%20pick%20for%20lounging%20around%20the%20house.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoka's%20Recovery%20Slides%20are%20originally%20intended%20for%20runners%20post-workout%2C%20which%20is%20why%20they%20feel%20as%20close%20to%20literally%20walking%20on%20a%20cloud%20as%20you%20can%20get.%20They're%20not%20the%20prettiest%20%E2%80%94%20although%20they%20definitely%20fall%20into%20the%20so-ugly-they're-cute%20category%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20just%20really%20doesn't%20matter%20when%20you%20are%20in%20serious%20pain%20around%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWearing%20supportive%20shoes%20around%20the%20house%20is%20crucial%3A%20Not%20only%20do%20many%20people%20feel%20a%20sharp%20or%20dull%20heel%20pain%20first%20thing%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20but%20your%20feet%20should%20be%20supported%20with%20every%20single%20step%2C%20which%20includes%20those%20around%20the%20house%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.austinregionalclinic.com%2Fdoctors%2Fkenneth-cornell%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDr.%20Cornell%2C%20DPM%3C%2Fa%3E%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%20and%20others%20struggling%20with%20this%20condition%2C%20barefoot%20time%20is%20a%20thing%20of%20the%20past.%20But%20with%20how%20soft%20and%20lightweight%20these%20Hoka%20Recovery%20Slides%20are%2C%20you%20won't%20mind%20the%20support.%20They%20feature%20an%20ultra-supportive%20outer%20layer%20of%20EVA%20foam%20which%20allows%20them%20to%20feel%20cushy%20to%20the%20touch.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20Recovery%20Slides%20are%20not%20as%20stiff%20as%20other%20footbeds%20but%20also%20aren't%20bendable%2C%20which%20is%20key%20according%20to%20our%20experts.%20They%20also%20integrate%20Hoka's%20signature%20rocking%20technology%2C%20and%20that%20rolling%20sensation%20with%20every%20step%20helps%20ease%20the%20pain%20in%20my%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20love%20that%20you%20can%20throw%20a%20pair%20of%20socks%20on%20with%20these%20slides%20in%20the%20winter%2C%20and%20that%20being%20made%20of%20foam%2C%20you%20can%20wear%20them%20in%20the%20shower%2C%20too.%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fauthor%2Falex-frost%5C%22%3EAlexandra%20Frost%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20freelance%20reporter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhat%20to%20look%20for%20when%20shopping%20for%20the%20best%20Hokas%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3ECushioning%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Not%20everyone%20wants%20or%20needs%20a%20well-cushioned%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Ffitness%2Fwhat-to-wear-running%5C%22%3Erunning%20shoe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20mid%20to%20max%20cushioning%20does%20help%20absorb%20the%20shock%20of%20running%20or%20walking%2C%20which%20can%20help%20reduce%20the%20impact%20on%20your%20joints%20and%20bones%20and%20make%20running%20more%20comfortable%20for%20beginners.%20It%20also%20helps%20minimize%20fatigue%20in%20your%20feet%20after%20standing%20all%20day.%20Hoka's%20shoes%20range%20in%20level%20of%20cushioning%2C%20with%20their%20lowest%20amount%20akin%20to%20mid%20cushioning%20in%20other%20brands.%20More%20cushioning%20means%20more%20comfort%2C%20but%20also%20comes%20at%20the%20price%20of%20a%20less-responsive%20push%20off%20of%20the%20ground%2C%20which%20some%20runners%20don't%20love.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EActivity%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Hoka%20shoes%20are%20great%20for%20most%20every%20activity%2C%20including%20running%2C%20walking%2C%20and%20hiking.%20For%20train%20running%20and%20hiking%2C%20you%20want%20a%20shoe%20with%20lugs%20to%20grip%20uneven%20terrain.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EStability%20vs.%20Neutral%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20When%20your%20foot%20strikes%20the%20ground%2C%20it%20either%20rolls%20inward%2C%20rolls%20outward%2C%20or%20stays%20pretty%20neutral.%20It's%20important%20to%20match%20your%20shoe's%20stability%20with%20your%20foot's%20natural%20roll%2C%20called%20pronation.%20If%20your%20shoes%20tend%20to%20wear%20down%20on%20the%20inside%20first%2C%20look%20for%20a%20stability%20model%20with%20support%20under%20your%20arch%20to%20counteract%20your%20overpronation%20(e.g.%2C%20Arahi%2C%20Gaviota).%20If%20your%20feet%20strike%20normal%20or%20supinate%2C%20look%20for%20a%20neutral%20model%20(e.g.%2C%20Bondi%2C%20Clifton).%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFoot%20conditions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Fbest-shoes-for-plantar-fasciitis%5C%22%3EMost%20experts%20recommend%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20well-cushioned%20and%20supportive%20shoe%20like%20Hoka%20for%20foot%20ailments%20such%20as%20plantar%20fasciitis%20and%20shin%20splints.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EFit%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Hokas%20notoriously%20fit%20all%20over%20the%20place%20from%20model%20to%20model%2C%20namely%20in%20the%20midfoot%20and%20toe%20box.%20Some%20run%20narrow%20and%20tighter%20all%20over%20(e.g.%2C%20Transport)%3B%20some%20run%20narrow%20in%20the%20midfoot%20and%20wide%20in%20the%20toe%20box%20(e.g.%2C%20Speedgoats)%3B%20and%20some%20are%20wide%20across%20the%20board%20(e.g.%2C%20Gaviota).%20Additionally%2C%20most%20models%20come%20in%20a%20regular%20and%20wide%20option.%20The%20inconsistency%20makes%20buying%20Hokas%20incredibly%20confusing.%20We%20highly%20recommend%20going%20to%20your%20local%20running%20store%20and%20trying%20the%20shoes%20on%20in%20person.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERetired%20Hokas%20we've%20tested%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHoka%20Bondi%20X%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMy%20go-to%20running%20and%20walking%20shoe%20for%20years%2C%20the%20Bondi%20X%20infused%20the%20beloved%20plush%20Bondi%20shoe%20with%20a%20propulsive%20carbon%20plate%20for%20a%20snappy%20push%20off%20the%20ground.%20Now%2C%20the%20closest%20model%20to%20this%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-72163-20%26h%3D9b13b56569d152b87291bf94db3c9445044adfc06ce16cc8c48e6d20ee36ee78%26postID%3D66a27796c79d31931d85ff02%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fstyle%252Fbest-hokas%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.hoka.com%252Fen%252Fus%252Fmens-everyday-running-shoes%252Fmach-x%252F1141450.html%253Fdwvar_1141450_color%253DWBGL%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMach%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20isn't%20as%20cushioned%20as%20the%20Bondi%20but%20has%20a%20similar%20snappy%20midsole%20plate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHoka%20Clifton%20Edge%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20This%20road%20shoe%20played%20off%20the%20Clifton's%20balanced%20cushioning%20and%20neutral%20stability%2C%20but%20debuted%20a%20super%20resilient%2C%20li