ta-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20Paloma%20in%20standard%20calf%5C%22%3EThe%20Paloma%20in%20standard%20calf%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20person%20modeling%20Inez%20Paloma%20shoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654bfec936d588dc55cd6e9c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Crozier%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20chic%20knee-high%20boot%20comes%20in%20three%20materials%3A%20black%20calf%20leather%2C%20brown%20suede%2C%20and%20shiny%20brown%20leather%20that's%20textured%20like%20crocodile%20skin.%20I%20opted%20for%20the%20crocodile%20option%2C%20which%20definitely%20looks%20very%20high-fashion%20in%20person.%20I%20like%20the%20idea%20that%20as%20the%20leather%20bends%20and%20gets%20softer%2C%20the%20creases%20will%20fit%20in%20nicely%20with%20the%20outside%20texture.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20with%20the%20Pilar%2C%20the%20padded%20footbed%20on%20this%20shoe%20makes%20all%20the%20difference%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20comfort.%20They're%20super%20easy%20to%20walk%20in%2C%20even%20though%20the%20heel%20is%203-inches%20high.%20And%20like%20most%20of%20Inez's%20boots%2C%20these%20fit%20true%20to%20size%20so%20you%20won't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20pinching%20or%20twisting%20due%20to%20sizing%20issues.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20one%20major%20issue%20that%20I%20had%20with%20this%20shoe%20is%20the%20height%20of%20the%20shaft.%20I'm%20five-foot-two%2C%20so%20my%20legs%20are%20a%20little%20shorter%20than%20average.%20This%20boot%20hit%20at%20the%20middle%20of%20my%20knee%2C%20which%20is%20a%20little%20unflattering.%20A%20knee-high%20boot%20should%20ideally%20hit%20right%20below%20the%20knee%20or%20a%20little%20lower.%20For%20context%2C%20I%20measured%20the%20shaft%20of%20these%20to%20be%20about%2015-inches%2C%20which%20is%20about%20average%20for%20knee-high%20boots.%20But%20for%20my%20height%2C%20I%20prefer%20it%20to%20be%20around%2013-inches.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20worked%20around%20this%20issue%20by%20pairing%20these%20with%20midi%20skirts%20that%20show%20off%20the%20boots%20while%20covering%20my%20knees.%20This%20is%20such%20a%20trendy%20way%20to%20wear%20boots%20that%20I%20don't%20mind.%20They%20also%20look%20pretty%20good%20with%20loose%20pants%2C%20but%20I%20avoid%20wearing%20them%20with%20mini%20skirts.%20And%20though%20there%20may%20not%20be%20different%20shaft%20heights%20available%2C%20there%20are%20two%20calf%20widths%20available.%20I%20opted%20for%20the%20standard%20calf%20version%2C%20which%20was%20a%20great%20fit.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20Paloma%20in%20extended%20calf%5C%22%3EThe%20Paloma%20in%20extended%20calf%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20full%20body%20perpective%20of%20someone%20wearing%20the%20Paloma%20extended%20calf%20boots%20next%20to%20a%20close%20up%20of%20someone's%20feet%20in%20the%20boot.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d47003cc84b4dfaffba09%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESally%20Kaplan%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20this%20pair%20of%20boots%2C%20my%20wife%20had%20to%20basically%20pick%20my%20jaw%20up%20off%20the%20ground.%20I%20mean%2C%20they're%20utterly%20gorgeous%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least.%20They%20also%20come%20in%20wide%20calf%20and%20footbed%20sizing%2C%20which%20just%20made%20me%20even%20more%20sure%20that%20someone%20designed%20these%20special%20for%20me.%20I%20get%20so%20many%20compliments%20every%20time%20I%20wear%20them%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20point%20that%20I've%20been%20buying%20outfits%20specifically%20to%20pair%20with%20these%20boots!%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20croc-embossed%20finish%20has%20a%20luxurious%20sheen%20to%20it%20that%20makes%20the%20boots%20look%20particularly%20elegant%2C%20and%20the%20texture%20and%20shine%20gives%20even%20the%20simplest%20sweater%20dress%20outfit%20a%20sophisticated%20flare.%20I%20love%20the%20brownish-burgundy%20pair%20I%20tested%2C%20but%20if%20you%20prefer%20a%20simpler%20look%20you%20can%20also%20opt%20for%20black%20leather%20or%20chestnut%20suede.%20Perhaps%20the%20biggest%20selling%20point%20was%20that%20I%2C%20a%20notorious%20heel%20hater%2C%20was%20able%20to%20wear%20these%20four%20hours%20on%20end%20while%20walking%20in%20the%20city%20thanks%20to%20the%20boots'%20well-constructed%20arch%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20drawback%20I%20can%20think%20of%20is%20one%20that%20every%20vertically%20challenged%20person%20who%20likes%20tall%20boots%20will%20understand%2C%20and%20that's%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20dig%20into%20the%20back%20of%20your%20knee%20on%20stairs.%20It's%20not%20uncommon%20for%20short%20people%20to%20struggle%20with%20knee-high%20boots%20on%20stairs%2C%20and%20it%20probably%20won't%20be%20an%20issue%20for%20you%20if%20you're%20over%205-foot-4%20or%20so.%20But%20at%205-foot-2%2C%20I%20always%20fall%20victim%20to%20the%20back-of-the-knee%20issue.%20Otherwise%2C%20the%20heel%20height%2C%20pitch%2C%20and%20wide-calf%20fit%2C%20and%20option%20for%20a%20wide%20footbed%20make%20everything%20about%20the%20boot%20super%20comfortable%20when%20you're%20standing%20still%20or%20walking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22The%20Mila%5C%22%3EThe%20Mila%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20side%20by%20side%20of%20a%20person%20modeling%20Inez%20Mila%20shoes.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654c008e36d588dc55cd7166%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESamantha%20Crozier%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Mila%20is%20the%20silhouette%20of%20the%20moment.%20I%20can't%20even%20tell%20you%20how%20many%20boots%20that%20look%20exactly%20like%20this%20I%20spotted%20on%20NYC's%20glitterati%20during%20fall%20fashion%20week.%20A%20pointed%20toe%2C%20a%20kitten%20heel%2C%20and%20a%20slouchy%20shaft%20have%20never%20been%20trendier%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20Mila%20combines%20them%20all.%20I%20got%20it%20in%20a%20luxurious%20black%20suede%2C%20but%20it's%20also%20available%20in%20olive%2C%20black%2C%20and%20silver%20leather.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20a%20perfect%20middle%20ground%20between%20knee-high%20boots%20and%20ankle%20boots.%20They%20hit%20right%20at%20the%20calf%20muscle%20on%20me%2C%20which%20I%20was%20worried%20would%20be%20unflattering%20since%20I%20don't%20have%20mile-long%20legs%20like%20the%20model.%20But%20they%20look%20amazing%20with%20tights.%20And%20I%20can't%20wait%20to%20wear%20them%20peeking%20out%20from%20maxi%20skirts%20and%20paired%20with%20slim-fitting%20pants.%20The%20only%20thing%20I%20would%20avoid%20wearing%20them%20with%20is%20mini%20skirts%20with%20bare%20legs%2C%20since%20they%20tend%20to%20emphasize%20the%20widest%20part%20of%20my%20leg.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAgain%2C%20I%20can't%20say%20enough%20good%20things%20about%20how%20comfortable%20these%20are.%20More%20than%20platforms%20or%20block%20heels%2C%20it%20takes%20a%20lot%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20kitten%20heels%20are%20comfortable%20and%20provide%20balance.%20And%20these%20pass%20the%20comfort%20test%20with%20flying%20colors.%20I%20would%20just%20caution%20anyone%20with%20particularly%20developed%20calf%20muscles%20that%20this%20may%20not%20work%20for%20them%2C%20since%20the%20shaft%20is%20a%20touch%20narrow.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Finez-review%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723666478000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F654d483a3cc84b4dfaffbb49%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstyle%2Finez-review%22%2C%22summ