0chilling%20details%20have%20emerged%20in%20the%20horrific%20rape-murder%20today%20with%20her%20parents%20claiming%20that%20their%20daughter%20was%20gang-raped.%20The%20petition%20said%20that%20the%20autopsy%20found%20150%20mg%20of%20semen%20in%20the%20victim's%20body%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20quantity%20suggesting%20involvement%20of%20more%20than%20one%20individual%2C%20further%20corroborated%20the%20suspicion%20of%20gang%20rape%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parents%20of%20the%20woman%20in%20their%20petition%20said%C2%A0that%20the%20postmortem%20report%20had%20unequivocally%20stated%20that%20the%20cause%20of%20death%20was%20strangulation%20of%20the%20neck%20and%20that%20there%20are%20clear%20signs%20of%20sexual%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20portions%20of%20the%20victim's%20head%20showed%20signs%20of%20trauma.%20%26quot%3BBoth%20ears%20exhibited%20signs%20of%20injury%2C%20suggesting%20a%20violent%20struggle.%20Her%20lips%20were%20injured%2C%20indicating%20that%20she%20may%20have%20been%20silenced%20or%20gagged%20during%20the%20attack%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20petition%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20said%20bite%20marks%20were%20found%20on%20her%20neck%2C%20underlining%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20assault.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20petition%20said%20that%20the%20autopsy%20found%20150%20mg%20of%20semen%20in%20the%20victim's%20body%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20quantity%20suggesting%20involvement%20of%20more%20than%20one%20individual%2C%20further%20corroborated%20the%20suspicion%20of%20gang%20rape%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20case%20was%20transferred%20to%20CBI%2C%20state%20police%20had%20arrested%20Sanjoy%20Roy%2C%20a%20civic%20volunteer%20who%20frequented%20the%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723661400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fjit6c758_college-street-protest_625x300_15_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpics-women-reclaim-the-night-demand-justice-in-kolkata-doctor-rape-murder-case-6339287%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Hundreds%20of%20women%20from%20across%20the%20country%20have%20taken%20to%20the%20streets%20to%20protest%20against%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BReclaim%20The%20Night%26quot%3B%3A%20Women%20Seek%20Justice%20In%20Kolkata%20Doctor%20Rape-Murder%20Case%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWomen%20in%20Kolkata%2C%20several%20parts%20of%20Bengal%2C%20and%20across%20cities%20in%20the%20country%20hit%20the%20streets%20tonight%20in%20protest%20against%20the%20horrific%20rape%20and%20murder%20of%20a%2031-year-old%20doctor%20at%20Kolkata's%20RG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital.%20The%20incident%20has%20shaken%20the%20country%20and%20triggered%20nationwide%20protests.%20At%20demonstrations%20in%20medical%20colleges%20and%20hospitals%20across%20the%20country%2C%20doctors%20have%20demanded%20security%20on%20duty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20protests%20across%20cities%20began%20at%2011.55%20pm.%20It%20has%20been%20described%20as%2C%20%26quot%3BFor%20women's%20independence%20on%20the%20midnight%20of%20independence%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPosters%20sharing%20locations%20of%20the%20protest%20were%20being%20shared%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20new%20spots%20being%20added%20as%20more%20and%20more%20people%20across%20Bengal's%20suburbs%20joined.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20protest%2C%20which%20has%20been%20named%2C%20%26quot%3BWomen%2C%20reclaim%20the%20night%26quot%3B%2C%20is%20also%20being%20staged%20outside%20Delhi's%20AIIMS%20and%20Chittaranjan%20Park.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20'reclaim%20the%20night'%20protests%20were%20organised%20in%20various%20parts%20of%20the%20country%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%202012%20gang-rape%20and%20murder%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20It%20All%20Started%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%20in%20Bengali%20media%2C%20researcher%20Rimjhim%20Sinha%20was%20the%20first%20to%20give%20a%20call%20for%20'reclaim%20the%20night'%20protest%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20the%20RG%20Kar%20incident.%20In%20a%20Facebook%20post%2C%20she%20had%20written%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20heard%20that%20Principal%20of%20RG%20Kar%20has%20said%20the%20doctor%20should%20not%20have%20wandered%20alone%20at%20night.%20I%20will%20be%20outside%20at%2011.55%20pm%20for%20my%20freedom.%20I%20will%20do%20what%20I%20want.%20I%20am%20not%20ready%20to%20listen%20to%20'night%20is%20not%20safe%20for%20women'%2C%20'the%20dress%20is%20not%20safe'%20and%20'the%20women%20does%20not%20have%20a%20good%20character'.%20I%20will%20spend%20the%20night%20outdoors.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERG%20Kar%20Medical%20College%20and%20Hospital's%20former%20Principal%20Dr%20Sandip%20Ghosh%2C%20who%20was%20pulled%20up%20by%20the%20Calcutta%20High%20Court%20for%20not%20being%20proactive%20after%20the%20doctor%20was%20found%20dead%20on%20campus%2C%20had%20earlier%20denied%20making%20such%20a%20remark.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20Facebook%20post%2C%20Rimjhim%20had%20invited%20people%20to%20join%20her%20near%20a%20bus%20stand%20in%20Jadavpur.%20She%20had%20not%20expected%20such%20a%20huge%20response.%20From%20one%20location%2C%20gatherings%20were%20planned%20at%20three.%20And%20the%20count%20crossed%20300%20before%20it%20transcended%20boundaries%20of%20the%20state.%20Men%2C%20too%2C%20joined%20the%20gatherings%20to%20express%20solidarity%20with%20the%20cause.%20Many%20celebrities%20have%20said%20they%20would%20be%20out%20tonight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKolkata%20sends%20a%20message%20of%20protest%20after%20any%20such%20incident.%20With%20that%20in%20mind%2C%20I%20had%20put%20out%20a%20post%20after%20speaking%20to%20friends%20and%20acquaintances.%20I%20had%20expected%20some%20of%20them%20to%20come.%20But%20I%20had%20no%20clue%20it%20would%20take%20this%20form%2C%26quot%3B%20Rimjhim%20told%20Anandabazar%20Patrika%20earlier%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20the%20tens%20of%20thousands%20expected%20to%20join%20the%20protest%20were%20quite%20a%20few%20celebrities%20too.%20Actors%20Swastika%20Mukherjee%20and%20Churni%20Ganguly%2C%20filmmakers%20Srijit%20Mukherji%2C%20Kaushik%20Ganguly%20and%20Pratim%20D%20Gupta%20and%20singer%20Iman%20Chakraborty%20had%20called%20upon%20people%20to%20join%20the%20midnight%20gathering%20at%20the%20meeting%20point%20most%20convenient%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKolkata%20Metro%20announced%20it%20will%20run%20additional%20trains%20because%20it%20has%20received%20requests%20from%20several%20quarters%20in%20view%20of%20the%20protests.%20Kolkata%20Bus-o-pedia%20said%20it%20will%20run%20free%20bus%20service%20for%20women%20tonight%20on%20several%20routes%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20History%20of%20Reclaim%20The%20Night%20Protests%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Take%20Back%20the%20Night%20rally%20was%20organised%20in%201975%20in%20US'%20Philadelphia%20after%20Susan%20Alexander%20Speeth%2C%20a%20young%20microbiologist%2C%20was%20stabbed%20to%20death%20when%20she%20was%20walking%20home%20at%20night.%20Two%20years%20later%2C%20such%20marches%20were%20organised%20in%20Germany%20to%20protest%20against%20violence%20against%20women.%20In%201977%2C%20women%20in%20Leeds%20took%20out%20a%20Reclaim%20the%20Night%20March%20to%20protest%20against%20police%20instructions%20to%20women%20to%20stay%20indoors%20after%20dark%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20a%20string%20of%20murders.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20such%20protests%20have%20been%20organised%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20world%20to%20protest%20against%20gender%20violence%20and%20victim-blaming.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723660440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fjglgkb88_kolkata-prot