rashtra's%20conduct%20in%20the%20matter%20was%20not%20that%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bmodel%20state%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20court%20warned%20it%20may%20direct%20that%20all%20the%20freebie%20schemes%20will%20be%20suspended%20until%20the%20compensation%20amount%20was%20paid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20bench%20of%20Justices%20BR%20Gavai%20and%20K%20V%20Viswanathan%20noted%20while%20the%20state%20has%20offered%20to%20pay%20Rs%2037.42%20crore%20as%20compensation%2C%20the%20applicant's%20counsel%20has%20contended%20that%20it%20comes%20to%20around%20Rs%20317%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdvocate%20Nishant%20R%20Katneshwarkar%2C%20appearing%20for%20Maharashtra%2C%20urged%20the%20bench%20to%20grant%20three%20weeks%2C%20saying%20the%20matter%20was%20being%20considered%20at%20the%20highest%20level%20and%20certain%20principle%20was%20required%20to%20be%20followed%20for%20calculating%20compensation%20according%20to%20the%20ready%20reckoner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20grant%20you%20three%20weeks%20time%20and%20pass%20an%20interim%20order%20that%20until%20we%20permit%2C%20no%20freebies%20schemes%20should%20be%20implemented%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Maharashtra.%20We%20will%20stop%20'Ladki%20Bahin'%2C%20'Ladka%20Bhau'%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20'Mukhyamantri%20Majhi%20Ladki%20Bahin%20Yojana'%20announced%20by%20the%20state%20government%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Rs%201%2C500%20is%20slated%20to%20be%20transferred%20into%20the%20bank%20accounts%20of%20eligible%20women%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2021%20to%2065%20years%20whose%20family%20income%20was%20less%20than%20Rs%202.5%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20under%20the%20'Ladka%20Bhau%20Yojana'%2C%20the%20scheme's%20primary%20goal%20is%20to%20provide%20financial%20assistance%20and%20practical%20work%20experience%20to%20young%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20hearing%2C%20Mr%20Katneshwarkar%20said%20he%20bowed%20to%20the%20directions%20passed%20by%20the%20court%20but%20due%20to%20such%20observations%2C%20headlines%20were%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMaybe.%20We%20are%20not%20bothered%20about%20it.%20We%20don't%20read%20newspapers.%20We%20are%20concerned%20about%20the%20rights%20of%20the%20citizens%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Gavai%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20it%20was%20constrained%20to%20make%20those%20observations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20thousands%20of%20crores%20of%20rupees%20to%20waste%20on%20freebies%20from%20the%20money%20of%20the%20public%20exchequer%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20have%20money%20to%20give%20to%20the%20person%20whose%20land%20has%20been%20deprived%20without%20following%20due%20process%20of%20law%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReferring%20to%20the%20earlier%20orders%20passed%20by%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20bench%20said%20it%20had%20recorded%20the%20%26quot%3Bglaring%20facts%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20noted%20since%20the%20court%20was%20not%20satisfied%20with%20the%20stand%20taken%20by%20the%20state%20in%20its%20affidavit%20filed%20on%20August%209%2C%20it%20had%20asked%20the%20state's%20counsel%20to%20discuss%20with%20the%20chief%20secretary%20and%20come%20out%20with%20a%20proposal%20which%20would%20at%20least%20be%20reasonable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20noted%20the%20land%20belonging%20to%20the%20applicant%20was%20illegally%20taken%20in%20possession%20by%20the%20state%20and%20later%20it%20was%20allotted%20to%20the%20Armament%20Research%20Development%20Establishment%20Institute%20(ARDEI).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20despite%20succeeding%20in%20the%20litigation%20right%20up%20to%20the%20top%20court%2C%20the%20applicant%20was%20required%20to%20run%20from%20pillar%20to%20post%20to%20get%20their%20legitimate%20due.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20not%20impressed%20with%20the%20submissions%20(of%20the%20state).%20If%20the%20state%20government%20wants%20to%20act%20with%20urgency%20in%20certain%20matters%2C%20the%20decisions%20are%20taken%20within%2024%20hours.%20However%2C%20we%20are%20inclined%20to%20give%20some%20more%20time%20to%20the%20state%20government%20to%20work%20out%20a%20reasonable%20compensation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20posted%20the%20matter%20for%20hearing%20on%20August%2028%20to%20enable%20the%20state%20to%20come%20out%20with%20proposal%20for%20grant%20of%20reasonable%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNeedless%20to%20state%20that%20if%20the%20state%20government%20does%20not%20come%20with%20such%20a%20proposal%20by%20that%20date%2C%20we%20will%20be%20compelled%20to%20pass%20such%20order%20as%20deemed%20fit%20and%20proper%20in%20the%20circumstances%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state's%20counsel%20said%20they%20be%20permitted%20to%20file%20an%20affidavit%20so%20that%20they%20can%20point%20out%20the%20steps%20taken%20by%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20the%20state%20may%20file%20an%20affidavit%20before%20the%20next%20date%20of%20hearing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20if%20we%20find%20that%20there%20is%20non-application%20of%20mind%20and%20he%20(applicant)%20is%20being%20harassed%E2%80%A6%20not%20only%20that%20we%20will%20direct%20all%20compensation%20to%20be%20paid%20as%20per%20the%20new%20Act%2C%20we%20will%20direct%20that%20until%20that%20amount%20is%20paid%2C%20all%20your%20freebie%20schemes%20will%20be%20suspended%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20warning%20you%20that%20if%20we%20don't%20find%20the%20stand%20to%20be%20genuine%2C%20apart%20from%20directing%20the%20compensation%20to%20be%20paid%20as%20per%20the%20new%20Act%2C%20the%20second%20direction%20will%20hit%20you%20more%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20hearing%20the%20matter%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20the%20court%20had%20asked%20the%20state%20to%20come%20up%20with%20a%20%26quot%3Breasonable%26quot%3B%20amount%20of%20compensation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20was%20hearing%20a%20matter%20related%20to%20the%20construction%20of%20buildings%20on%20forest%20land%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20where%20a%20private%20party%20has%20succeeded%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20to%20get%20possession%20of%20the%20land%20that%20was%20%26quot%3Billegally%20occupied%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20government%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20said%20piece%20of%20land%20was%20occupied%20by%20the%20ARDEI%2C%20a%20unit%20of%20the%20Centre's%20Defence%20Department.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20said%20subsequently%2C%20another%20piece%20of%20land%20was%20allotted%20to%20the%20private%20party%20in%20lieu%20of%20the%20land%20that%20was%20in%20the%20ARDEI's%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20later%20it%20was%20found%20that%20the%20land%20allotted%20to%20the%20private%20party%20was%20notified%20as%20forest%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20July%2023%20order%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20private%20party%2C%20which%20has%20succeeded%20up%20to%20the%20top%20court%2C%20cannot%20be%20denied%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20decree%20passed%20in%20his%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723653960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Ftatqdjeo_supreme-court_625x300_08_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-suspend-all-freebies-until-compensation-is-paid-to-private-party-sc-warns-maharashtra-govt-6336977%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Wednesday%20warned%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20that%20it%20would%20suspend%20its%20freebie%20schemes%20unless%20it%20pays%20compensation%20to%20a%20private%20party%20whose%20land%20was%20%26quot%3Billegally%26quot%3B%20occupied%20by%20it%20more%20than%20six%20decades%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BInhumane%26quot%3B%3A%20After%20Vinesh's%20Appeal%20Gets%20Rejected%2C%20IOA%20Explores%20Legal%20Option%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20massive%20heart-break%20for%20India%2C%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20petition%20for%20a%20joint%20Olympic%20silver%20medal%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20was%20rejected%20by%20the%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20for%20Sport%20(CAS)%20on%20Wednesday.%20Vinesh%20had%20entered%20the%20final%20of%20the%20women's%2050kg%20wrestling%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20after%20some%20great%20bouts%2C%20which%20included%20win%20against%20Japanese%20world%20champions%20Yui%20Susaki.%20However%2C%20on%20the%20morning%20of%20her%20final%2C%20Vinesh%20was%20found%20to%20be%20100%20gram%20overweight%20than%20the%20permissible%20limit%2C%20and%20hence%20she%20was%20disqualified.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20CAS's%20verdict%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20which%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20application%20filed%20by%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20on%207%20August%202024%20is%20dismissed%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20Indian%20Olympic%20Association%20(IOA)%20reacted%20in%20a%20strong%20way%20saying%20they%20were%20exploring%20all%20possible%20options.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIOA%20president%20PT%20Usha%20has%20expressed%20her%20shock%20and%20disappointment.%20%26quot%3BThe%20operative%20part%20of%20the%20August%2014%20decision%2C%20which%20dismisses%20Vinesh's%20application%20to%20be%20awarded%20a%20shared%20silver%20medal%20women's%2050%20kg%20category%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympic%20Games%202024%2C%20has%20significant%20implications%20for%20her%20in%20particular%20and%20the%20sporting%20community%20at%20large%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IOA%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThe%20marginal%20discrepancy%20of%20a%20100%20grams%20and%20the%20resultant%20consequences%20has%20profound%20impact%2C%20not%20only%20in%20terms%20of%20Vinesh's%20career%20but%20also%20raises%20serious%20questions%20about%20ambiguous%20rules%20and%20their%20interpretation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20IOA%20firmly%20believes%20that%20the%20total%20disqualification%20of%20an%20athlete%20for%20such%20a%20weight%20infraction%20on%20the%20second%20of%20two%20days%20warrants%20a%20deeper%20examination.%20Our%20legal%20representatives%20had%20duly%20brought%20this%20out%20in%20their%20submissions%20before%20the%20Sole%20Arbitrator.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA%20called%20for%20a%20change%20in%20the%20rule%20to%20take%20into%20account%20player's%20well-being.%20It%20added%20that%20further%20legal%20options%20were%20being%20explored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20involving%20Vinesh%20highlights%20the%20stringent%20and%2C%20arguably%2C%20inhumane%20regulations%20that%20fail%20to%20account%20for%20the%20physiological%20and%20psychological%20stresses%20athletes%2C%20particularly%20female%20athletes%2C%20undergo.%20It%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20need%20for%20more%20equitable%20and%20reasonable%20standards%20that%20prioritize%20athletes'%20well-being%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IOA%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20order%20of%20the%20CAS%2C%20the%20IOA%20continues%20to%20stand%20in%20full%20support%20of%20Ms.%20Phogat%20and%20is%20exploring%20further%20legal%20options.%20The%20IOA%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20that%20Vinesh's%20case%20is%20heard.%20It%20will%20continue%20to%20advocate%20justice%20and%20fairness%20in%20sports%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20rights%20and%20dignity%20of%20athletes%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20sports%20fold%20are%20upheld%20at%20all%20times.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWe%20appreciate%20the%20continued%20support%20and%20understanding%20of%20our%20stakeholders%2C%20athletes%2C%20and%20the%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723653900000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fqlqpvubg_vinesh-phogat_625x300_13_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com