es%20had%20duly%20brought%20this%20out%20in%20their%20submissions%20before%20the%20Sole%20Arbitrator%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20IOA%20said%20in%20its%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20matter%20involving%20Vinesh%20highlights%20the%20stringent%20and%2C%20arguably%2C%20inhumane%20regulations%20that%20fail%20to%20account%20for%20the%20physiological%20and%20psychological%20stresses%20athletes%2C%20particularly%20female%20athletes%2C%20undergo.%20It%20is%20a%20stark%20reminder%20of%20the%20need%20for%20more%20equitable%20and%20reasonable%20standards%20that%20prioritize%20athletes'%20well-being.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IOA%20further%20said%20that%20it%20would%20provide%20any%20possible%20assistance%20to%20Vinesh%20going%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20light%20of%20the%20order%20of%20the%20CAS%2C%20the%20IOA%20continues%20to%20stand%20in%20full%20support%20of%20Ms.%20Phogat%20and%20is%20exploring%20further%20legal%20options.%20The%20IOA%20is%20committed%20to%20ensuring%20that%20Vinesh's%20case%20is%20heard.%20It%20will%20continue%20to%20advocate%20justice%20and%20fairness%20in%20sports%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20rights%20and%20dignity%20of%20athletes%20and%20everyone%20in%20the%20sports%20fold%20are%20upheld%20at%20all%20times.%26quot%3B%20the%20IOA%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20appreciate%20the%20continued%20support%20and%20understanding%20of%20our%20stakeholders%2C%20athletes%2C%20and%20the%20public.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723652340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2F7356ds3k_vinesh-phogat-ani_640x480_09_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fvinesh-phogats-petition-for-silver-in-olympics-2024-dismissed-by-court-of-arbitration-for-sport-source-6338393%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Heartbreak%20for%20India%20as%20Wrestler%20Vinesh%20Phogat's%20petition%20for%20joint%20silver%20medal%20in%20Olympics%202024%20has%20been%20dismissed%20by%20Court%20of%20Arb