pUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fdisgusting-british-influencer-slammed-for-putting-underwear-between-breads-in-supermarket%2Famp_articleshow%2F112531356.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNot%20Appropriate%20For%20Me...%26quot%3B%3A%20Praful%20Patel%20On%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20'Admission'%20On%20Wife%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20day%20after%20it%20was%20reported%20that%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar%20had%20'admitted'%20that%20he%20had%20made%20a%20mistake%20by%20fielding%20his%20wife%20Sunetra%20against%20his%20cousin%20Supriya%20Sule%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20senior%20NCP%20leader%20Praful%20Patel%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20it%20would%20not%20be%20appropriate%20for%20him%20to%20comment%20on%20this%20because%20it%20was%20Mr%20Pawar's%20family%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sule%2C%20who%20is%20the%20daughter%20of%20NCP%20(Sharadchandra%20Pawar)%20chief%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20had%20defeated%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20in%20the%20Baramati%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20by%20a%20margin%20of%20over%201.5%20lakh%20votes.%20Ajit%20Pawar%2C%20who%20had%20split%20the%20NCP%20and%20joined%20the%20government%20run%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20faction%20of%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20last%20year%2C%20had%20turned%20the%20contest%20for%20the%20family%20bastion%20of%20Baramati%20into%20a%20prestige%20battle%20by%20picking%20his%20wife%20as%20the%20candidate.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20his%20faction%20of%20the%20NCP%2C%20which%20had%20retained%20the%20name%20and%20symbol%20of%20the%20party%2C%20won%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%2C%20the%20group%20led%20by%20his%20uncle%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20managed%20to%20bag%20eight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20decision%20to%20field%20Sunetra%20Pawar%20against%20Ms%20Sule%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20had%20told%20a%20Marathi%20news%20channel%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20all%20my%20sisters.%20One%20shouldn't%20allow%20politics%20to%20enter%20homes.%20I%20made%20a%20mistake%20in%20fielding%20Sunetra%20against%20my%20sister.%20This%20shouldn't%20have%20happened.%20But%20the%20parliamentary%20board%20(of%20NCP)%20made%20a%20decision.%20Now%20I%20feel%20it%20was%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Praful%20Patel%2C%20who%20had%20stood%20shoulder%20to%20shoulder%20with%20Ajit%20Pawar%20during%20the%20rebellion%20against%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20was%20asked%20about%20the%20statement%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20his%20personal%20matter%2C%20his%20family's%20matter.%20He%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%20in%20the%20state%20and%20the%20president%20of%20our%20party%2C%20the%20NCP.%20If%20he%20has%20said%20something%2C%20then%20I%20do%20not%20think%20it%20is%20appropriate%20for%20me%20to%20say%20anything%20more%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20he%20would%20visit%20Ms%20Sule%20on%20Raksha%20Bandhan%20next%20week%2C%20Mr%20Pawar%20had%20said%20that%20while%20he%20is%20on%20tour%2C%20he%20would%20try%20and%20meet%20his%20sisters%20if%20they%20are%20in%20one%20place.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMaharashtra%20Minister%20Deepak%20Kesarkar%20said%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20should%20not%20mix%20family%20with%20politics.%20As%20a%20brother%2C%20it%20is%20his%20(Ajit%20Pawar's)%20duty%20to%20go%20and%20celebrate%20Rakshabandhan.%20Also%2C%20as%20a%20political%20leader%2C%20he%20would%20be%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20Mahayuti%20(the%20coalition%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20Shiv%20Sena%20(Eknath%20Shinde%20Faction)%20and%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar-led%20NCP)%20to%20win%20elections.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723652160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fi2delhq4_ajit-pawar-with-wife-sunetra-pawar-at-an-election-rally-ians_625x300_13_August_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnot-appropriate-for-me-praful-patel-on-ajit-pawars-admission-on-