A%22Culture%20Secretary%20Govind%20Mohan%20Appointed%20New%20Home%20Secretary%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Centre%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Govind%20Mohan%2C%20who%20is%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%2C%20will%20be%20the%20next%20Home%20Secretary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mohan%20has%20been%20appointed%20as%20an%20Officer%20on%20Special%20Duty%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20with%20immediate%20effect%20and%20will%20take%20over%20from%20the%20current%20Home%20Secretary%2C%20Ajay%20Kumar%20Bhalla%2C%20when%20his%20term%20ends%20on%20August%2022.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bhalla%2C%20a%201984-batch%20IAS%20officer%20of%20the%20Assam-Meghalaya%20cadre%2C%20was%20appointed%20the%20Union%20Home%20Secretary%20in%20August%202019%20and%20remained%20in%20the%20post%20for%20nearly%20half%20a%20decade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr%20Bhalla%20is%20one%20of%20the%20longest-serving%20Home%20Secretaries%20at%20the%20Centre.%20As%20per%20rules%2C%20he%20could%20not%20have%20given%20another%20extension%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20official%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20official%20said%20that%20the%20tenures%20of%20the%20Home%20Secretary%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Intelligence%20Bureau%2C%20the%20CBI%20Director%2C%20Defence%20Secretary%2C%20Foreign%20Secretary%20and%20Cabinet%20Secretary%20were%20fixed%20for%20two%20years%20but%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20amended%20this%20and%20added%20two%20more%20years%2C%20and%20then%20an%20additional%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20if%20another%20extension%20was%20to%20be%20given%20to%20Mr%20Bhalla%2C%20another%20administrative%20order%20would%20be%20needed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mohan%2C%20who%20turns%2059%20next%20month%2C%20is%20taking%20over%20at%20a%20crucial%20time%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Assembly%20elections%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%2C%20which%20are%20likely%20to%20be%20announced%20soon.%20An%20electrical%20engineer%20from%20IIT(BHU)%20Varanasi%2C%20Mr%20Mohan%20has%20been%20the%20Union%20Culture%20Secretary%20since%20October%202021%20and%20has%20also%20worked%20in%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20in%20the%20past%20-%20%C2%A0as%20a%20Joint%20Secretary%20from%20May%20to%20September%202018%20and%20as%20Additional%20Secretary%20from%20September%202018%20to%20September%202021%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20he%20has%20been%20on%20Central%20Deputation%20since%20August%202017.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723650060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fq4pb5vh_secretary-culture_625x300_14_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fculture-secretary-govind-mohan-appointed-new-home-secretary-6337853%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20announced%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20Govind%20Mohan%2C%20who%20is%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Culture%2C%20will%20be%20the%20next%20Home%20Secretary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fculture-secretary-govind-mohan-appointed-new-home-secretary-6337853%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Barron%20Trump's%20friend%20is%20asked%20why%20Gen%20Z%20would%20vote%20for%20Donald.%20His%2020-second%20reply%20is...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723650039000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112530909%2Cimgsize-1004616.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-barron-trumps-friend-is-asked-why-gen-z-would-vote-for-donald-his-20-second-reply-is-%2Farticleshow%2F112530907.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F112530907.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EBarron%20Trump's%