%20men%20named%20Harjeet%20Singh%20and%20Satish%20Rao%20have%20been%20accused%20of%20assisting%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20female%20victims%20said%20she%20met%20Mohit%20on%20the%20matrimonial%20website%20Shaadi.com%20and%20that%20he%20promised%20to%20marry%20her%20and%20take%20her%20to%20Canada.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20sold%20all%20my%20household%20items%20in%20Ludhiana%2C%20I%20have%20become%20homeless.%20Everything%20happened%20within%20a%20few%20days.%20Actually%2C%20his%20behaviour%20was%20very%20good.%20Ask%20anyone%20if%20there%20was%20even%20one%20percent%20doubt.%20No%20one%20doubted%20that%20person%2C%26quot%3B%20Surinder%20Kaur%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUpon%20realising%20that%20they%20had%20been%20cheated%2C%20the%20victims%2C%20left%20without%20any%20money%20or%20mobile%20phones%2C%20spent%20the%20night%20at%20Lonavala%20railway%20station%20before%20filing%20a%20complaint%20with%20the%20police.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20were%20told%20in%20the%20morning%20that%20we%20have%20to%20have%20an%20interview%20in%20the%20embassy%2C%20so%20he%20asked%20us%20to%20give%20him%20our%20phones.%20Everyone%20was%20given%20something%20mixed%20in%20mango%20shake%2C%20it%20was%20very%20strong%2C%20after%20that%20we%20did%20not%20know%20anything.%20Everyone%20fell%20asleep%20suddenly%2C%20the%20boys%20were%20unconscious.%20After%20that%2C%20around%205%20o'clock%2C%20Harjeet%20Singh%20and%20Suresh%20Rao%20took%20the%20goods%20in%20an%20auto.%20We%20also%20have%20the%20number%20of%20the%20auto%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20of%20the%20victims%2C%20Neha%20Malhotra%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaji%20Arora%2C%20who%20had%20Rs%207.5%20lakh%20taken%20out%20of%20her%20account%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20this%20transfer%20was%20done.%20After%20the%20transfer%20we%20came%20to%20know%20that%20they%20had%20left%20with%20the%20luggage.%20When%20we%20checked%20the%20CCTV%2C%20Mohit%20had%20left%20at%2012%20o'clock.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20mobile%20phones%20are%20switched%20off%20right%20now%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20out%20their%20CDR%20(Call%20Detail%20Records)%2C%20the%20woman%20had%20also%20met%20him%20in%20Santa%20Cruz%2C%20so%20we%20are%20taking%20her%20information.%20Today%20is%20only%20the%20first%20day%20of%20the%20investigation%2C%20so%20we%20cannot%20say%20much%20at%20the%20moment%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Police%20Inspector%20Suhas%20Jagtap%20of%20Lonavala%20City%20Police%20Station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20a%20Nicaragua-bound%20plane%20was%20grounded%20in%20France%20after%20it%20was%20allegedly%20used%20for%20a%20'donkey%20flight'.%20Officials%20at%20the%20time%20had%20said%20that%20299%20of%20the%20plane's%20303%20passengers%20were%20Indian.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20flight's%20connection%20to%20Nicaragua%20raised%20eyebrows%2C%20as%20the%20central%20American%20nation%20has%20seen%20a%20surge%20in%20individuals%20seeking%20asylum%20in%20the%20United%20States.%20According%20to%20data%20from%20the%20US%20Customs%20and%20Border%20Patrol%20(CBP)%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20significant%20increase%20in%20Indians%20attempting%20to%20enter%20the%20US%20illegally%2C%20with%2096%2C917%20recorded%20in%20the%20fiscal%20year%202023%2C%20representing%20a%2051.61%20per%20cent%20jump%20from%20the%20previous%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723647060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fmuro6fng_canada-toronto_625x300_14_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdunki-agent-promises-job-to-7-steals-phones-cash-in-maharashtra-6337469%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20travel%20agent%20has%20fled%20after%20cheating%20nine%20people%2C%20including%20a%20woman%20and%20her%20two%20children%2C%20out%20of%20cash%20and%20mobile%20phones%20in%20Maharashtra%20after%20promising%20to%20send%20them%20to%20Canada%20using%20the%20illegal%20%26quot%3BDonkey%20Flight%26quot%3B%20route.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdunki-agent-promises-job-to-7-steals-phones-cash-in-maharashtra-6337469%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Acting%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20Chief%20Rahul%20Navin%20Appointed%20Full-Time%20Head%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActing%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20chief%20Rahul%20Navin%20has%20been%20appointed%20full-time%20director%20of%20the%20anti-money%20laundering%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20order%20issued%20by%20the%20Appointments%20Committee%20of%20the%20Cabinet%20(ACC)%20said%20the%20appointment%20of%20Mr%20Navin%2C%20a%201993-batch%20Indian%20Revenue%20Service%20(IRS)%20officer%20of%20the%20Income%20Tax%20cadre%2C%20has%20been%20made%20%26quot%3Bfor%20a%20period%20of%20two%20years...%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20director%20is%20an%20Additional%20Secretary%20(AS)%20rank%20post%20in%20the%20Union%20government%20and%20Mr%20Navin%20was%20empanelled%20as%20an%20AS%20in%20December%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Navin%2C%2057%2C%20joined%20the%20ED%20in%20November%2C%202019%20as%20a%20Special%20Director%20(OSD)%20to%20spearhead%20the%20agency's%20work%20on%20India's%20mutual%20evaluation%20by%20the%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20(FATF)%2C%20the%20global%20body%20that%20leads%20action%20against%20money%20laundering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20a%20BTech%20and%20an%20MTech%20from%20IIT%20Kanpur%20and%20an%20MBA%20from%20the%20Swinburne%20University%20of%20Technology%20in%20Melbourne.%20He%20was%20appointed%20acting%20director%20of%20the%20ED%20after%20the%20tenure%20of%20his%20predecessor%20Sanjay%20Kumar%20Mishra%20ended%20in%20September%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidered%20close%20to%20Mr%20Mishra%2C%20Mr%20Navin's%20tenure%20as%20the%20ED%20head%20saw%20the%20high-profile%20arrests%20of%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Jharkhand%20Chief%20Minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20in%20separate%20money%20laundering%20cases.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20expert%20in%20international%20taxation%20matters%2C%20Mr%20Navin%20belongs%20to%20Bihar%20and%20has%20worked%20in%20the%20I-T%20department%20for%2030%20years.%20During%20his%20stint%20in%20the%20international%20taxation%20wing%20from%202004-08%2C%20the%20I-T%20department%20raised%20demands%20on%20several%20offshore%20transactions%20including%20in%20the%20Vodafone%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Navin%20had%20rushed%20to%20West%20Bengal%20after%20an%20ED%20team%20was%20attacked%20in%20Sandeshkhali%20and%20had%20asked%20his%20investigators%20to%20%26quot%3Bwork%20without%20fear%26quot%3B%20and%20prepare%20a%20watertight%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IRS%20officer%20has%20authored%20various%20international%20taxation%20and%20transfer%20pricing%20journals%20and%20articles%20in%20the%20I-T%20department%20that%20are%20taught%20to%20trainee%20IRS%20officers%20at%20their%20alma%20mater%2C%20the%20National%20Academy%20of%20Direct%20Taxes%20(NADT)%20in%20Nagpur%2C%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20investigates%20financial%20crimes%20under%20two%20criminal%20laws%20--%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20and%20the%20Fugitive%20Economic%20Offenders%20Act%20(FEOA)%20apart%20from%20the%20civil%20provisions%20of%20the%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Management%20Act%20(FEMA).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723646400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-09%2Fo97nfik8_rahul-navin_625x300_15_September_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-navin-enforcement-directorate-chief-acting-enforcement-directorate-chief-rahul-navin-appointed-full-time-head-6337745%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Centre%20has%20appointed%20Rahul%20Navin%2C%2057%2C%20presently%20serving%20as%20a%20Special%20Director%20in%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20as%20the%20full-time%20director%20of%20the%20agency%20for%20two%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frahul-navin-enforcement-directorate-chief-acting-enforcement-directorate-chief-rahul-navin-appointed-full-time-head-6337745%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BAffirmative%20Action%20Must%20Be%20Strengthened%20As%20Instrument%20Of%20Inclusion%26quot%3B%3A%20President%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20nation%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%2078th%20Independence%20Day%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20made%20a%20push%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20society%20and%20called%20for%20affirmative%20action%20to%20be%20strengthened%20as%20an%20instrument%20towards%20this%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20various%20schemes%2C%20including%20the%20distribution%20of%20free%20foodgrains%20to%20over%2080%20crore%20people%2C%20the%20President%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20social%20justice%20is%20the%20top%20priority%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murmu%20said%20that%20witnessing%20the%20unfurling%20of%20the%20tricolour%20at%20the%20Red%20Fort%2C%20in%20state%20capitals%20or%20local%20neighbourhoods%20thrills%20the%20hearts%20of%20citizens%20and%20is%20an%20expression%20of%20the%20joy%20of%20being%20part%20of%20our%20great%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20as%20we%20celebrate%20various%20festivals%20with%20our%20families%2C%20we%20celebrate%20Independence%20Day%20and%20Republic%20Day%20with%20our%20family%20that%20comprises%20our%20fellow%20citizens...%20We%20realise%20that%20we%20are%20part%20of%20a%20chain%20that%20binds%20the%20dreams%20of%20those%20who%20participated%20in%20the%20freedom%20struggle%20and%20the%20aspirations%20of%20those%20who%20will%20witness%20the%20nation%20regaining%20its%20full%20glory%20in%20the%20years%20to%20come.%20Realising%20that%20we%20are%20links%20of%20this%20chain%20of%20history%20is%20humbling%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaluting%20the%20supreme%20sacrifices%20of%20freedom%20fighters%20which%20awakened%20the%20%26quot%3Bsoul%20of%20India%20from%20centuries%20of%20torpor%26quot%3B%20and%20remembering%20the%20dark%20days%20of%20partition%2C%20Ms%20Murmu%20said%20the%20government%20is%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20enable%20India%20to%20reclaim%20its%20rightful%20position%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECongratulating%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20voters%2C%20officials%2C%20security%20forces%20and%20everybody%20else%20involved%20in%20this%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20President%20said%20it%20was%20the%20largest%20electoral%20exercise%20humankind%20has%20ever%20witnessed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia's%20successful%20conduct%20of%20elections%20strengthens%20democratic%20forces%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20President%20asserted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEconomic%20Strength%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Murmu%20said%20that%20between%202021%20and%202024%2C%20India%20has%20been%20among%20the%20fastest-growing%20major%20economies%2C%20with%20an%20average%20annual%20growth%20rate%20of%208%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20has%20not%20only%20put%20more%20money%20in%20the%20hands%20of%20people%2C%20but%20has%20also%20drastically%20reduced%20the%20number%20of%20people%20living%20below%20the%20poverty%20line.%20As%20for%20those%20who%20continue%20to%20suffer%20from%20poverty%2C%20all%20efforts%20are%20being%20made%20to%20not%20only%20provide%20a%20helping%20hand%20to%20them%2C%20but%20also%20bring%20them%20out%20of%20it.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20PM%20Garib%20Kalyan%20Anna%20Yojana%20continues%20to%20provide%20free%20ration%20to%2080%20crore%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20President%20said%20India%20is%20the%20fifth%20largest%20economy%20in%20the%20world%20and%20is%20poised%20to%20become%20one%20of%20the%20top%20three%20economies%20soon.%20For%20this%2C%20she%20credited%20the%20hard%20work%20of%20farmers%20and%20workers%2C%20the%20farsightedness%20of%20planners%20and%20wealth%20creators%2C%20and%20a%20visionary%20leadership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20the%20government%20has%20created%20an%20ideal%20ecosystem%20for%20startups%20and%20made%20India%20an%20%26quot%3Beven%20more%20attractive%26quot%3B%20investment%20destination%2C%20Ms%20Murmu%20added%2C%20%26quot%3BAll%20of%20these%20factors%20have%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20of%20economic%20reforms%20and%20economic%20growth%20that%20will%20catapult%20India%20among%20the%20developed%20nations.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723646160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-08%2Fh5h3il6g_droupadi-murmu_625x300_14_August_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faffirmative-action-must-be-strengthened-as-instrument-of-inclusion-president-6337380%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Addressing%20the%20nation%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%2078th%20Independence%20Day%2C%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%20made%20a%20push%20for%20a%20more%20inclusive%20society%20and%20called%20for%20affirmative%20action%20to%20be%20strengthened%20as%20an%20instrument%20of%20inclusion.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Faffirmative-action-must-be-strengthened-as-instrument-of-inclusion-president-6337380%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Harris%20campaign%20editing%20news%20headlines%20in%20her%20favour%20within%20Google%20search%20ads%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723646032000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-112529875%2Cimgsize-1236485.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fharris-campaign-editing-news-headlines-in-her-favour-within-google-search-ads-report%2Fartic