mer%20from%20the%20Discom.%20Accordingly%2C%20consumers%20receive%20a%20net%20import%2Fexport%20bill%20from%20the%20Discom%20as%20per%20the%20net%20consumption%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20two%20meters%20in%20this%20configuration%3A%20the%20solar%20energy%20meter%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263424%2Fharyana-farmer-innovation-solar-panel-trolley-portable-for-sale%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20generated%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20bidirectional%20energy%20meter%2C%20which%20measures%20the%20export%20and%20import%20of%20energy%20from%2Fto%20the%20consumer%E2%80%99s%20premises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20end%2C%20what%20the%20consumer%20receives%20is%20a%20net%20electricity%20bull%20indicating%20either%20a%20net%20export%20to%20the%20main%20grid%20or%20a%20net%20import%20from%20the%20grid.%20So%2C%20the%20consumer%20ends%20up%20paying%20(or%20not%20paying)%20the%20difference%20between%20the%20electricity%20consumed%20from%20the%20discom%20and%20the%20electricity%20generated%20by%20the%20solar%20power%20system%20that%20is%20sent%20back%20to%20the%20grid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20electricity%20my%20solar%20panels%20produce%20is%20being%20sold%20back%20to%20the%20DHBVN.%20One%20of%20their%20employees%20comes%20to%20note%20down%20readings%20on%20two%20electric%20meters%20installed%20at%20home%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-Solar-Panes-1723448587.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22electricity%20bill%20is%20significantly%20lower%20thanks%20to%20a%20transition%20to%20solar%20power%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-Solar-Panes-1723448587.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-Solar-Panes-1723448587-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-Solar-Panes-1723448587-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-Solar-Panes-1723448587-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-Solar-Panes-1723448587-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360800%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EGoing%20solar%20has%20significantly%20reduced%20Sandeep%20Mall%E2%80%99s%20electricity%20bill.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Sandeep%20saw%20the%20benefit%20of%20installing%20the%2010%20kW%20rooftop%20solar%20system%2C%20he%20decided%20to%20install%20a%20further%2015%20kW%20to%20fulfil%20his%20household%E2%80%99s%20needs%20about%20a%20year%20ago.%20%E2%80%9CToday%2C%20we%20have%20a%2025%20kW%20rooftop%20solar%20connection%20at%20home.%20This%20summer%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20benefit%20of%20installing%20such%20a%20system%20at%20home%20with%20our%20total%20electricity%20bill%20over%20two%20peak%20summer%20months%20(June%20and%20July)%20coming%20to%20less%20than%20Rs%2013%20from%20the%20usual%20summertime%20bill%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20to%20install%20a%20rooftop%20solar%20system%20was%20essentially%20inspired%20by%20escalating%20power%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20solar%20was%20the%20in-thing%2C%20and%20a%20lot%20of%20our%20friends%20and%20family%20were%20installing%20it.%20Since%20we%20were%20already%20incurring%20such%20large%20electricity%20bills%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20try%20it%20out%20even%20though%20the%20capital%20cost%20of%20installing%20it%20at%20the%20time%20was%20quite%20expensive%20than%20what%20it%20is%20today.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20initially%20installed%20a%2010%20kW%20system%20before%20embarking%20on%20installing%20another%2015%20kW%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20the%20costs%20of%20installing%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rooftop%20solar%20power%20unit%20Sandeep%20set%20up%20came%20from%20Tata%20Power%20and%20they%20helped%20him%20set%20it%20up.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20cost%20me%20around%20Rs%2060%2C000%20per%20kW%20to%20install%20our%20first%2010%20kW%20system.%20However%2C%20the%20capital%20cost%20of%20installing%20such%20a%20system%20has%20reduced%20substantially%2C%20while%20the%20quality%20and%20power%20output%20of%20the%20panels%20that%20I%20installed%20in%20the%20second%20phase%20have%20also%20improved.%20When%20I%20installed%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20my%20rooftop%20solar%20power%20system%2C%20it%20cost%20me%20around%20Rs%2045%2C000%20per%20kW%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Sandeep.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20installing%20the%20solar%20panels%2C%20there%20was%20some%20minor%20construction%20work%20that%20needed%20to%20be%20done%20at%20his%20residence%20like%20setting%20up%20the%20foundation.%20%E2%80%9COnce%20the%20panels%20we%20ordered%20came%20from%20their%20%5BTata%20Power%5D%20manufacturing%20facility%2C%20it%20hardly%20took%20two%20days%20to%20install%20it.%20The%20company%20also%20helped%20with%20all%20the%20formalities%20and%20permissions%20documentation%20required%20by%20the%20state%20electricity%20board.%20We%20faced%20no%20hassles%20in%20installing%20this%20plug-and-play%20rooftop%20solar%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20much%20does%20it%20cost%20to%20maintain%20the%20solar%20power%20system%3F%20Many%20of%20the%20issues%20surrounding%20the%20cost%20of%20installing%20solar%20come%20with%20maintenance%20and%20after-sales%20service.%20But%2C%20as%20Sandeep%20explains%2C%20there%20are%20two%20ways%20to%20approach%20installing%20a%20rooftop%20solar%20system%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1)%20People%20store%20the%20power%20they%20generate%20from%20their%20rooftop%20solar%20system%20in%20a%20battery%20storage%20system%20and%20use%20that%20%5Bpower%5D%20to%20run%20their%20home.%20Maintaining%20and%20managing%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F343975%2Felectric-vehicle-battery-nanocarbon-using-coconut-waste-jaipur-cancrie-akshay-jain-mahi-singh%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebattery%20storage%3C%2Fa%3E%20system%20is%20expensive%20because%20you%20have%20to%20change%20batteries%20every%20few%20years%20and%20space%20is%20needed%20for%20it.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20what%20happens%20is%20that%20neither%20you%20(the%20consumer)%20are%20buying%20the%20power%20nor%20are%20you%20selling%20it.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20whatever%20power%20you%20generate%2C%20you%E2%80%99re%20saving%20it%20in%20your%20battery%20storage%20system%20like%20an%20inverter%20does%2C%20and%20then%20using%20it%20to%20run%20electrical%20appliances%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2)%20The%20second%20approach%20is%20the%20one%20he%20has%20taken%2C%20i.e.%20employing%20net%20metering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20I%20have%20not%20incurred%20any%20maintenance%20cost%20or%20called%20for%20external%20help.%20We%20have%20set%20up%20cleaning%20showers%20on%20the%20rooftop.%20We%20manually%20turn%20on%20the%20tap%2C%20and%20these%20showers%20clear%20all%20the%20dust%20collected%20on%20these%20panels.%20This%20accumulated%20dust%20reduces%20the%20output%20that%20your%20panel%20is%20capable%20of%20generating.%20In%20the%20NCR%20region%2C%20dust%20pollution%20levels%20are%20high%2C%20and%20our%20panels%20need%20frequent%20cleaning.%20We%20deploy%20these%20cleaning%20showers%20every%20three%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20is%20there%20a%20plan%20soon%20to%20eventually%20make%20that%20transition%20to%20depend%20on%20solar%20power%20and%20energy%20to%20run%20your%20appliances%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-1-1723448690.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandeep%20Mall's%20cheaper%20electricity%20bill%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-1-1723448690.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-1-1723448690-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-1-1723448690-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-1-1723448690-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-1-1723448690-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-360801%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESandeep%20Mall%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNo%2C%20as%20I%20explained%20earlier%2C%20there%20are%20recurring%20costs%20involved%20with%20managing%20the%20battery%20storage%20system.%20More%20than%20that%2C%20however%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20is%20also%20required%20to%20service%20these%20batteries%20and%20ensure%20everything%20runs%20smoothly%2C%20which%20I%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20many%20have%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20capital%20expenditure%20(capex)%20that%20is%20required%20to%20set%20it%20up%20and%20running.%20Did%20he%20avail%20of%20any%20government%20subsidy%20to%20set%20this%20up%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20the%20first%20phase%20we%20installed%2C%20the%20solar%20panel%20installers%20took%20the%20responsibility%20of%20acquiring%20the%20subsidy%20from%20the%20government%20that%20helped%20us%20cover%20some%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20installing%20it.%20Today%2C%20however%2C%20you%20have%20a%20variety%20of%20subsidy%20and%20low-interest%20loan%20schemes%20to%20help%20you%20pay%20the%20cost%20of%20purchasing%20and%20installing%20a%20rooftop%20solar%20system.%20Each%20state%20has%20its%20schemes%20to%20incentivise%20residents%20and%20companies%20into%20installing%20their%20rooftop%20solar%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%E2%80%99s%20more%2C%20Sandeep%20argues%20that%20there%20is%20a%20real%20return%20on%20investment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20invested%20between%20Rs%2012%20lakh%20to%20Rs%2013%20lakh%20on%20installing%20the%2025%20kW%20system%20%5Bgiven%20that%20I%20spent%20on%20average%20Rs%2050%2C000%20per%20kilowatt%20to%20install%20it%5D.%20My%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F356491%2Fpune-aundh-couple-harness-solar-power-to-run-air-conditioner-ac-bungalow-reduce-electricity-water-bills%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eannual%20savings%20in%20electricity%20bills%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20approximately%20Rs%203%20lakh%20to%20Rs%204%20lakh.%20So%2C%20in%20the%20next%20two%20to%20three%20years%2C%20I%20will%20recover%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20investment%20I%20made%20into%20installing%20this%20system.%20From%20the%20fourth%20year%20%5Bsince%20installing%20the%20system%5D%20onwards%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20plain%20sailing%20and%20there%20is%20a%2025-year%20warranty%20attached%20to%20my%20system%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20Sandeep%20Mall)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1723451497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FSandeep-Mall-Solar-Panels-02-1723448506.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D360791%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sandeep%20Mall%2C%20a%20Faridabad-based%20entrepreneur%20and%20wellness%20coach%2C%20installed%20a%20rooftop%20solar%20system%20and%20employed%20a%20net%20metering%20mechanism%20to%20manage%20his%20electricity%20bills%20for%20a%2010%2C000%2B%20sq%20ft%20home.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Rinchen%20Norbu%20Wangchuk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F360791%2Frooftop-solar-system-net-metering-to-reduce-electricity-bill-sandeep-mall-entreprenuer%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20a%20Techie%20Brought%20Corporates%20%26amp%3B%20Communities%20Together%20to%20Revive%2040%20Wells%20%26amp%3B%206%20Lakes%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20sponsored%20by%20SayTrees%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20temperatures%20soaring%20to%2041.8%20degrees%20Celsius%2C%20Bengaluru%20broke%20all%20its%20previous%20records%20this%20year%2C%20making%20it%20one%20of%20the%20hottest%20years%20in%20the%20last%20five%20decades.%20This%20was%20not%20the%20Bengaluru%20that%20Kapil%20Sharma%20treasures%20in%20his%20heart.%20Originally%20from%20Raipur%2C%20Chhattisgarh%2C%20Kapil%20first%20came%20to%20the%20city%20in%202001%20for%20his%20engineering%20studies%20and%20immediately%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20its%20beauty%20and%20greenery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBack%20home%20in%20Raipur%2C%20we%20would%20spend%20our%20days%20filling%20water%20in%20the%20air%20coolers%20to%20combat%20the%20scorching%20heat.%20But%20Bengaluru%20was%20different%20back%20then.%20I%20remember%20coming%20to%20take%20an%20entrance%20exam%20at%20a%20school%20where%20the%20exam%20centre%20had%20no%20fans.%20It%20was%20strange%20for%20me%20to%20see%20a%20place%20without%20fans.%20While%20it%20would%20be%2045%20degrees%20in%20Raipur%2C%20it%20would%20rain%20in%20Bengaluru.%20It%20rained%20almos