rmance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Hindustan%20Times%20article%20mentioned%20that%20Sreejesh%20believes%20a%20goalkeeper%20should%20be%20a%20%E2%80%98crazy%20person%E2%80%99%20and%20must%20know%20the%20art%20of%20intimidating.%20%E2%80%9CCrazy%2C%20because%20you%20just%20need%20to%20have%20the%20guts%20to%20stand%20in%20front%20of%20that%20ball.%20The%20second%20thing%20is%20aggression%3B%20you%20need%20to%20be%20an%20aggressive%20person%2C%20and%20those%20reflexes%20have%20to%20be%20there.%20You%20don%E2%80%99t%20get%20much%20time%20to%20just%20think%2C%20%E2%80%98Save%E2%80%99.%20No%2C%20you%20just%20need%20to%20save%20it.%20Then%20you%20realise%2C%20%E2%80%98Okay%2C%20I%20made%20that%20save%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20acted%20as%20the%20wall%20of%20the%20Indian%20hockey%20team%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20the%20lonely%20tusker%20is%20now%20representing%20India%20one%20last%20time%20at%20the%20Paris%20Olympics.%20The%20country%20hopes%20for%20a%20medal%20as%20the%20ultimate%20farewell%20for%20its%20greatest%20goalkeeper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWatch%20this%20video%20to%20learn%20more%20about%20PR%20Sreejesh%E2%80%99s%20journey%3A%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FQaJju-vhXek%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26rel%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D1%26controls%3D1%26color%3Dred%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%