%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20they%20have%20also%20planted%20%E2%80%98nitrogen%20fixer%E2%80%99%20plants%20like%20mustard%20and%20clover%2C%20which%20are%20also%20used%20for%20mulching.%20The%20Bansal%20family%20also%20does%20mulching%20thrice%20a%20year%20with%20the%20grass%20grown%20in%20their%20orchard.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMulching%20is%20an%20agricultural%20practice%20where%20an%20area%20of%20soil%20is%20covered%20with%20grass%20and%20other%20farm%20waste%20which%20decomposes%20and%20improves%20the%20soil%20health.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20did%20a%20course%20in%20permaculture%20from%20Aranya%20Agricultural%20Alternatives%20in%20Hyderabad.%20Permaculture%20(permanent%20agriculture)%20is%20the%20harmonious%20integration%20of%20nature%20and%20humans%3B%20where%20one%20lives%20with%20nature%2C%20instead%20of%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPermaculture%20is%20a%20way%20of%20living.%20Today%2C%20most%20people%20follow%20monocropping.%20Take%20a%20look%20at%20any%20forest%2C%20you%E2%80%99ll%20find%20different%20kinds%20of%20plants%20growing%20together.%20No%20jungle%20will%20have%20just%20one%20plant%20or%20animal.%20Soil%20health%20and%20quality%20is%20spoilt%20because%20of%20monoculture.%20If%20you%20grow%20different%20crops%20together%2C%20even%20if%20one%20is%20spoiled%2C%20the%20other%20will%20survive%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Aprajita.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20explains%20that%20the%20soil%20health%20improves%20as%20well.%20She%20is%20now%20working%20on%20creating%20a%20food%20forest%20on%20a%20small%20portion%20of%20her%20parents%E2%80%99%20land.%20Here%2C%20she%20is%20growing%20different%20varieties%20of%20native%20trees%20and%20plants.%20She%20collects%20heirloom%20seeds%20from%20across%20the%20country%20and%20grows%20them%20in%20their%20orchard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20remains%20confident%20that%20the%20soil%20will%20be%20in%20great%20condition%20in%20the%20next%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20the%20apples%20are%20more%20prone%20to%20insect%20bites%20now%20and%20many%20get%20damaged%2C%20I%E2%80%99m%20satisfied%20that%20we%20are%20giving%20poison-free%20fruits%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Aprajita%2C%20for%20whom%20life%20has%20indeed%20come%20full%20circle.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20Aprajita%20Bansal%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722939423000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F08%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-47-min-1722938835.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D359926%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Aprajita%20Bansal%20runs%20Phal%20Phool%2C%20a%20startup%20that%20sells%20apples%20and%20other%20products%20grown%20on%20her%20family%20orchard%20in%20Banon%2C%20Himachal%20Pradesh.%20By%20eliminating%20middlemen%2C%20she%20has%20ensured%20that%20her%20father%20earns%20three%20times%20the%20profit%20while%20customers%20get%20farm%20fresh%20apples.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F359926%2Fhimachal-apples-order-online-farming-aprajita-bansal-phal-phool-d2c-fresh-produce-no-middlemen%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Southwest%20Airlines%20Shakes%20Up%20Its%20Seating%20Rules%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Southwest%20Airlines%20will%20also%20offer%20redeye%20flights%20for%20the%20first%20time.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721905992000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fimg.huffingtonpost.com%2Fasset%2F66a2323a2400008f135480a1.jpeg%3Fcache%3DpzSvOdxBTd%26ops%3D1200_630%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fairlines-results_n_66a23238e4b0ac6125bd8d5b%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Southwest%20Airlines%20will%20also%20offer%20redeye%20flights%20for%20the%20first%20time.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A189%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.huffpost.com%2Fentry%2Fairlines-results_n